3Atext%3DAs%2520reported%2520in%2520The%2520Wire%2C%2525%2520of%2520the%2520write%252Doffs.%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Ehere%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Chr%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20no%20money%2C%20moneylenders%20are%20not%20ready%20to%20wait.%20What%20should%20we%20do%3F%20We%20can%E2%80%99t%20even%20afford%20to%20take%20onions%20to%20the%20market.%20You%20are%20just%20thinking%20about%20yourself%2C%20Modi%20saheb.%20You%20must%20provide%20the%20guaranteed%20price%20for%20the%20produce%E2%80%A6%20The%20finance%20guys%20threaten%2C%20and%20the%20%3C%2Fem%3Epatpedhi%3Cem%3E%20(cooperative%20society)%20officers%20abuse.%20Who%20should%20we%20go%20for%20justice%3F%E2%80%A6%20Today%2C%20I%20am%20forced%20to%20commit%20suicide%20because%20of%20your%20inaction.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThose%20were%20the%20words%20of%20Dashrath%20Lakshman%20Kedari%20before%20he%20died%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fcities%2Fpune%2Fmaharashtra-farmer-suicide-note-blaming-pm-modi-8159289%2F%5C%22%3Esuicide%3C%2Fa%3E%20last%20year%20in%20Pune%20district%20of%20Maharashtra.%20His%20is%20one%20among%20the%201%2C00%2C474%20suicides%20in%20the%20farming%20sector%20in%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20years%20(2014-2022)%2C%20as%20per%20the%20recently%20released%20National%20Crime%20Records%20Bureau%20(NCRB)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fncrb.gov.in%2Faccidental-deaths-suicides-in-india-year-wise.html%3Fyear%3D2022%26keyword%3D%5C%22%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E.%20This%20amounts%20to%20nearly%2030%20suicides%20per%20day%20in%20these%20nine%20years.%20And%20yet%20we%20heard%20BJP%20MP%20Nishikant%20Dubey%20claiming%20that%20no%20farmer%20has%20died%20under%20Modi%20by%20suicide.%20%E2%80%9CDid%20the%20opposition%20ever%20have%20a%20single%20discussion%20about%20farmers%E2%80%99%20suicides%20in%20the%20last%20eight%20years%3F%E2%80%9D%20he%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Ffact-check-bjp-mp-nishikant-dubey-farmer-suicides%5C%22%3Easked%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CIf%20they%20didn%E2%80%99t%2C%3Cem%3E%20it%20means%20farmers%20are%20not%20dying%20by%20suicide.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20death%20of%20the%20kisan%2C%20like%20the%20jawan%20or%20say%20corruption%2C%20has%20been%20one%20of%20those%20emotive%20subjects%20that%20has%20a%20bearing%20on%20the%20moral%20compass%20of%20the%20nation.%20The%20noose%20around%20the%20neck%20of%20the%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3Eannadata%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%20has%20generally%20been%20a%20subject%20that%20arouses%20sentiments.%20But%20sadly%20the%20revelations%20of%20the%20present%20NCRB%20report%20does%20not%20seem%20to%20have%20evoked%20any%20such%20moral%20outrage%20in%20the%20media%20or%20on%20primetime%20debates.%20This%20is%20despite%20the%20fact%20that%20in%20the%20second%20term%20of%20the%20Modi%20government%2C%20the%20total%20farmer%20suicides%20increased%20in%20absolute%20numbers%20from%2010%2C281%20to%2011%2C290.%20Within%20this%2C%20the%20rise%20in%20the%20number%20of%20suicides%20among%20agricultural%20workers%20seems%20to%20be%20much%20sharper%2C%20from%204%2C324%20to%206%2C083%20i.e.%2041%25.%20Maharashtra%2C%20with%20the%20ill-fated%20regions%20of%20Vidharbha%20and%20Marathwada%2C%20yet%20again%20witnessed%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fagriculture%2Fmore-than-2300-farmer-suicides-in-10-months-in-maharashtra%5C%22%3Eworst%3C%2Fa%3E%20situation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F17163446%2FFS1.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22936%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F17163446%2FFS1.png%20936w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F17163446%2FFS1-300x135.png%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-689564%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22422%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20saw%20quite%20a%20direct%20and%20rather%20bold%20reference%20to%20the%20issue%20in%20a%20recent%20Bollywood%20movie%2C%20%3Cem%3EJawan%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20wherein%20a%20peasant%20family%20dealing%20with%20crop%20failure%20was%20having%20to%20face%20the%20wrath%20of%20loan%20recovery%20agents%20of%20the%20bank%2C%20finally%20leading%20up%20to%20the%20father%20taking%20his%20own%20life.%20The%20segment%20in%20the%20movie%20alludes%20to%20systemic%20and%20policy%20level%20shifts%20that%20have%20contributed%20to%20the%20crisis.%20And%20if%20one%20does%20down%20the%20rabbit%20hole%2C%20the%20reasons%20go%20back%20to%20the%20structural%20shifts%20that%20were%20written%20into%20the%20neoliberal%20decades%20that%20ensued%20in%20the%20early%201990s.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDeclining%20public%20investments%2C%20privatisation%20of%20key%20industries%2C%20opening%20up%20to%20external%20trade%2C%20decline%20in%20state%20subsidies%20and%20shrinking%20formal%20agricultural%20credit%20all%20contributed%20to%20the%20long%20winter%20for%20farmers%20in%20India%20who%20found%20it%20increasingly%20difficult%20to%20compete%20with%20the%20heavily%20subsidised%20imports.%20Add%20to%20this%20the%20monopolistic%20practices%20of%20agro-business%20giants%20like%20Monsanto%2C%20the%20expensive%2C%20out%20of%20reach%20genetically%20modified%20seeds%2C%20fertilisers%20and%20insecticides%20that%20raised%20inputs%20cost%20by%20leaps.%20The%20deadly%20combination%20left%20the%20farmers%20exposed%20to%20the%20vagaries%20of%20both%20the%20monsoon%20and%20the%20market%2C%20with%20recovery%20agents%20lurking%20in%20the%20shadows.%20The%20crudest%20manifestation%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.himalmag.com%2Fneoliberalism-green-revolution-agrarian-distress-farmers-india%2F%5C%22%3Ecrisis%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20been%20the%203%2C50%2C000%20suicides%20in%20the%20farming%20sector%20in%20the%20three%20decades%20since%20liberalisation.%20The%20historic%20farmers%E2%80%99%20agitation%20against%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-india-54233080%5C%22%3Efarm%20Bills%3C%2Fa%3E%20pushed%20by%20the%20Modi%20government%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20was%20a%20desperate%20fight%20back%20against%20what%20was%20being%20touted%20as%20Indian%20farming%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9C1991%20moment%E2%80%9D.%20The%20Bills%20would%20have%20made%20farmers%20directly%20negotiate%20with%20private%20corporations%20instead%20of%20the%20mediation%20of%20a%20state-regulated%20market%20place.%20It%20took%20about%20750%20deaths%20and%20a%20year-long%20militant%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F750-died-during-farmers-protest-no-condolence-from-centre-rakesh-tikait-2602504%5C%22%3Eagitation%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20the%20government%20to%20finally%20retreat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20poll%20campaign%20in%202014%20Modi%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DKYSGC9vL8aA%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9COur%20farmers%20must%20not%20be%20pushed%20to%20take%20the%20noose%2C%20our%20farmers%20should%20not%20have%20to%20take%20heavy%20loans%2C%20they%20should%20not%20be%20forced%20to%20knock%20on%20the%20doors%20of%20the%20sahukar.%20Isn%E2%80%99t%20it%20the%20responsibility%20of%20the%20government%20and%20the%20banks%20that%20they%20give%20credits%20to%20the%20farmers%3F%20And%20if%20the%20conditions%20of%20the%20farmers%20improve%20it%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20only%20improve%20for%20them%2C%20it%20gives%20employment%20to%20many%20who%20work%20the%20fields.%E2%80%9D%20The%20rising%20suicides%20among%20farmers%2C%20particularly%20agricultural%20workers%2C%20however%2C%20paint%20a%20different%20and%20much%20darker%20reality%20in%20the%20fields.%20In%20terms%20of%20indebtedness%2C%20the%20government%20claims%20that%20the%20percentage%20of%20indebted%20farmers%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pib.gov.in%2FPressReleasePage.aspx%3FPRID%3D1753856%5C%22%3Ereduced%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%2052%25%20in%202013%20to%2050.2%25%20in%202019.%20However%2C%20we%20can%20see%20marked%20increase%20in%20both%20absolute%20numbers%20of%20farmers%20indebted%20i.e.%20from%20902%20lakh%20to%20930%20lakh%20in%20the%20same%20period%2C%20and%20also%20the%20average%20amount%20of%20outstanding%20loan%20saw%20an%20upsurge%20of%20about%201.6%20times%20than%202013.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F17163519%2FFS2.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22936%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F17163519%2FFS2.png%20936w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F17163519%2FFS2-300x119.png%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-689565%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22372%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ESource%3A%20MOSPI%2C%20Situation%20Assessment%20Survey%20of%20Agricultural%20Households%20and%20Land%20and%20Livestock%20Holdings%20of%20Households%20of%20various%20years%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20suicide%20notes%20of%20the%20likes%20of%20Dashrath%20Kedari%20clearly%20point%20towards%20the%20political%20message%20in%20such%20suicides.%20Daniel%20M%C3%BCnster%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20maintains%20that%20farmers%E2%80%99%20suicides%20intend%20to%20do%20more%20than%20just%20end%20a%20life%3A%20%E2%80%9Cthey%20convey%20a%20message%20of%20despair%20and%20protest%20and%2C%20therefore%2C%20a%20political%20message.%E2%80%9D%20Sainath%E2%80%99s%20unravelling%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findiatogether.org%2Fmids4-op-ed%23%3A~%3Atext%3DOn%2520average%252C%2520one%2520farmer%2520took%2Cthese%2520states%252C%2520writes%2520P%2520Sainath.%26amp%3Btext%3DOn%2520average%252C%2520one%2520Indian%2520farmer%2Cone%2520suicide%2520every%252030%2520minutes.%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9Cpesticide%20suicides%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%202000s%20seemed%20to%20carry%20a%20message.%20After%20all%2C%20for%20farmers%2C%20expensive%20pesticides%20are%20often%20the%20reason%20for%20their%20indebtedness.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20attempt%20by%20neoliberal%20governance%20has%20been%20to%20steadily%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Facademic.oup.com%2Fips%2Farticle-abstract%2F13%2F1%2F37%2F5214542%3FredirectedFrom%3Dfulltext%5C%22%3Edepoliticise%3C%2Fa%3E%20farmers%E2%80%99%20suicides%20and%20strip%20them%20of%20any%20deeper%20messaging.%20They%20have%20done%20this%20by%20either%20individualising%20or%20pathologising%20suicides%20as%20a%20psychological%20or%20mental%20health%20problem%20rather%20than%20an%20economic%20issue.%20So%2C%20the%20response%20is%20often%20in%20the%20shape%20of%20mental%20health%20support%20that%20effectively%20blames%20the%20farmers%2C%20and%20thereby%20teaches%20them%20%E2%80%9Cself-reliance%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cself-respect%E2%80%9D.%20Or%20we%20see%20corporate%20social%20responsibility%20programmes%20(run%20by%20the%20same%20corporate%20giants%20like%20Monsanto%20that%20have%20led%20to%20the%20crisis)%20who%20stress%20upon%20the%20need%20to%20educate%20the%20farmers%20on%20how%20to%20embrace%20a%20%E2%80%9Cneoliberal%20entrepreneurial%20mentality%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20malice%2C%20as%20articulated%20by%20farmers%20unions%2C%20activists%20(and%20even%20by%20Shah%20Rukh%20Khan%20in%20the%20movie%20%3Cem%3EJawan%3C%2Fem%3E)%2C%20is%20in%20fact%20systemic.%20A%20glance%20through%20some%20of%20the%20numbers%20in%20the%20Modi%20years%20does%20give%20us%20the%20necessary%20perspective%20to%20understand%20how%20the%20crisis%20is%20perpetuated%20consciously.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F17164103%2FFS3.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22979%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F17164103%2FFS3.png%20979w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F17164103%2FFS3-300x130.png%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-689568%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22424%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ESource%3A%20Demand%20for%20grants%20of%20the%20Union%20government%2C%20Annual%20Budget.%20Note*%3A%20FY%202019-20%20to%20FY%202021-22%20includes%20Actual%20estimates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20is%20evident%20in%20the%20graph%20above%2C%20public%20expenditure%20on%20agriculture%20in%20relation%20to%20total%20budget%20expenditure%20has%20been%20falling%20step%20by%20step%20in%20the%20Modi%202.0%20years.%20And%20so%20has%20the%20share%20allocated%20for%20farmers%E2%80%99%20welfare.%20The%20crisis%20can%20also%20be%20fathomed%20by%20looking%20at%20the%20growth%20rate%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fopinion%2Fcolumns%2Fjean-dreze-writes-wages-are-the-worry-not-just-unemployment-8553226%2F%5C%22%3Ereal%20wages%3C%2Fa%3E%20between%202014-15%20and%202021-22%20which%20has%20been%20below%201%25%20per%20year%20across%20the%20board%2C%20including%20for%20agricultural%20labour.%20The%20impact%20is%20clear%20in%20alarmingly%20low%20rural%20demand%2C%20which%20constitutes%20nearly%2036%25%20of%20FMCG%20sales.%20In%20the%20Confederation%20of%20Indian%20Industry%E2%80%99s%20FMCG%20summit%2C%20the%20managements%20of%20various%20FMCG%20companies%20raised%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Frural-income-stress-cloud-over-fmcg-demand%5C%22%3Econcern%3C%2Fa%3E%20about%20rural%20demand%20that%20%E2%80%9Cremained%20under%20pressure%20because%20incomes%20were%20under%20stress%20in%20rural%20areas%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20allocation%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiabudget.gov.in%2F%5C%22%3EMahatma%20Gandhi%20National%20Rural%20Employment%20Guarantee%20Act%3C%2Fa%3E%20(MGNREGA)%2C%20that%20serves%20as%20a%20lifeline%20in%20such%20times%20of%20distress%2C%20has%20been%20seeing%20its%20allocations%20dwindling%20over%20the%20years.%20It%20plummeted%20from%201.85%25%20of%20the%20overall%20budget%20in%20FY%202014-15%20to%20a%20mere%201.33%25%20in%20FY%202023-24%2C%20representing%20a%20historical%20low.%20The%20current%20allocation%20of%20Rs%2060%2C000%20crore%20marks%20a%20substantial%2033%25%20decrease%20from%20the%20previous%20year%20and%20is%20only%200.198%25%20of%20the%20total%20GDP.%20Exclusionary%20measures%2C%20including%20Aadhaar-based%20payment%20systems%2C%20have%20affected%2057%25%20of%20workers%2C%20and%20despite%20the%20scheme%E2%80%99s%20goal%20of%20providing%20100%20days%20of%20employment%2C%20only%203%25%20secure%20it%2C%20raising%20concerns%20about%20effective%20implementation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20crucial%20agricultural%20schemes%20need%20to%20be%20tested%20against%20reality%2C%20such%20as%20the%20Pradhan%20Mantri%20Fasal%20Bima%20Yojana%20(PMFBY)%2C%20Market%20Intervention%20Scheme%20and%20the%20Price%20Support%20Scheme%20(MIS-PSS)%2C%20and%20Pradhan%20Mantri%20Kisan%20Samman%20Nidhi%20(PM-Kisan).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20allocation%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiabudget.gov.in%2F%5C%22%3EPMFBY%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20consistently%20increased%20over%20the%20years%2C%20reaching%20Rs%2015%2C500%20crore%20in%20the%20Budget%20Estimate%20for%202022-2023.%20Despite%20the%20programme%E2%80%99s%20voluntary%20nature%20and%20comprehensive%20risk%20coverage%2C%20the%20data%20as%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpib.gov.in%2FPressReleaseIframePage.aspx%3FPRID%3D1984068%5C%22%3ENovember%2030%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20reveals%20a%20substantial%20surge%20in%20farmer%20applications%2C%20with%20435%20lakh%20and%20689%20lakh%20enrolled%20during%20the%20Rabi%202022-23%20and%20Kharif%202023%20seasons%2C%20respectively.%20However%2C%20the%20scheme%E2%80%99s%20effectiveness%20is%20questionable%2C%20as%20evidenced%20by%20the%20rather%20low%20number%20of%20claims%20paid%20%E2%80%93%20amounting%20to%20just%20Rs%203%2C878%20crore%20for%20just%207.8%20lakh%20farmers%20in%20the%20Rabi%202022-23%20season.%20This%20raises%20concerns%20about%20the%20programme%E2%80%99s%20ability%20to%20provide%20meaningful%20support%20to%20the%20majority%20of%20applicants.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiabudget.gov.in%2F%5C%22%3EPradhan%20Mantri%20Kisan%20Samman%20Nidhi%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20seen%20a%20substantial%20increase%20to%20Rs%2068%2C000%20crore%20in%20the%20Budget%20Estimate%20for%202022-2023%2C%20the%20scheme%20primarily%20benefits%20land-owning%20farmers%20and%20overlooks%20the%20needs%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findia.mongabay.com%2F2023%2F01%2Fclimate-change-vulnerabilities-pushing-landless-farmers-to-the-brink%2F%5C%22%3Elandless%20agricultural%20labourers%3C%2Fa%3E.%20A%20one-size-fits-all%20approach%20is%20not%20suitable%20for%20the%20diverse%20agricultural%20landscape%20in%20India%2C%20as%20shown%20in%20the%20NCRB%20report%20where%20the%20number%20of%20deaths%20of%20landless%20agricultural%20labour%20has%20increased%20since%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20the%20reduced%20Budget%20Estimate%20of%20Rs%201%2C500%20crore%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiabudget.gov.in%2F%5C%22%3EMIS-PSS%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202022-2023%20raises%20questions%20about%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20commitment%20to%20addressing%20market%20price%20disparities.%20Earlier%20this%20year%2C%20in%20June%2C%20the%20government%20announced%20the%20Minimum%20Support%20Price%20(MSP)%20for%2017%20%E2%80%98kharif%E2%80%99%20crops%2C%20including%20paddy%2C%20pulses%20(moong%2C%20arhar%2C%20urad)%2C%20oilseeds%20like%20groundnut%20and%20soybean%2C%20and%20cotton.%20However%2C%20the%20declared%20MSP%20has%20been%20deemed%20insufficient%20by%20various%20farmer%E2%80%99s%20groups.%20When%20indexed%20to%20rising%20inflation%2C%20the%20MSP%20has%20clearly%20failed%20to%20protect%20small%20farmers%20against%20indebtedness.%20The%20government%20is%20still%20far%20from%20its%202014%20poll%20promise%20of%20aligning%20the%20MSP%20with%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fruralindiaonline.org%2Fen%2Farticles%2Fall-reports-by-the-swaminathan-commission%2F%5C%22%3ESwaminathan%20Commission%3C%2Fa%3E%20recommendations%20and%20doubling%20farmers%E2%80%99%20income.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEmpty%20rhetoric%2C%20failing%20schemes%20and%20inadequate%20allocations%20are%20pushing%20the%20%E2%80%9Cannadatas%E2%80%9D%20of%20our%20country%20into%20deep%20despair.%20The%20haunting%20surge%20in%20farmer%20suicides%20under%20this%20regime%20is%20symptomatic%20of%20the%20systemic%20neglect.%C2%A0%20The%20climate%20crisis%2C%20which%20again%20has%20been%20exacerbated%20by%20decades%20of%20growth-mania%20under%20neoliberalism%2C%20poses%20yet%20another%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscience.thewire.in%2Feconomy%2Fagriculture%2Fclimate-crisis-is-foundation-of-indian-farmers-protests%2F%5C%22%3Echallenge%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20the%20farmers%20in%20despair%20as%20they%20are%20faced%20with%20crop%20failures%20due%20to%20heat%20waves%2C%20lower%20yield%20and%20devastating%20extreme%20weather%20events.%20The%20relentless%20struggle%20against%20financial%20burdens%2C%20manifold%20uncertainties%2C%20coupled%20with%20rising%20inflation%20and%20a%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Fif-there-was-political-will-indias-raging-cost-of-living-crisis-could-be-eased%5C%22%3Ecost%20of%20living%20crisis%3C%2Fa%3E%20demands%20a%20fundamental%20shift%20in%20policies%20if%20we%20are%20to%20rectify%20this%20dance%20of%20death.%20As%20pointed%20out%20by%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fsc-takes-govt-to-task-over-farmer-suicides%2Farticle17405881.ece%5C%22%3ESupreme%20Court%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20instead%20of%20going%20to%20the%20roots%20of%20the%20issue%2C%20merely%20cosmetic%20measures%2C%20like%20post%20facto%20compensation%20to%20the%20family%20of%20the%20deceased%2C%20are%20far%20from%20enough.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAnirban%20Bhattacharya%20is%20the%20Team%20Lead%20for%20the%20National%20Finance%20Team%2C%20Pranay%20Raj%20is%20a%20Data%20Analyst%20and%20Nancy%20Pathak%20is%20a%20Researcher%20in%20the%20National%20Finance%20Team%20at%20the%20Centre%20for%20Financial%20Accountability.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702863033000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F17165434%2Fhari-gaddigopula-xZEYonpj41o-unsplash.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fagriculture%2Faverage-30-farmer-suicides-per-day-in-modi-govt-years-points-to-a-systemic-apathy%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20attempt%20by%20neoliberal%20governance%20has%20been%20to%20steadily%20depoliticise%20farmers'%20suicides%20and%20strip%20them%20of%20any%20deeper%20messaging.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fagriculture%2Faverage-30-farmer-suicides-per-day-in-modi-govt-years-points-to-a-systemic-apathy%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22End%20'culture%20of%20hatred'%2C%20says%20mother%20of%20boy%20shot%20in%20US%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702863018000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2FDC25%2Fproduction%2F_132075365_roryswimm.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fuk-scotland-67694134%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Glasgow-born%20Susan%20Swimm's%2023-year-old%20son%20Rory%20was%20shot%20dead%20by%20a%20teenager%20in%20Utah%20in%20October.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A23%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fuk