ill%20Us%20All%26quot%3B%3A%20Gaza%20Hospital%20In%20Rubble%20After%20Israeli%20Withdrawal%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20what%20was%20once%20the%20courtyard%20of%20the%20Kamal%20Adwan%20hospital%20in%20the%20northern%20Gaza%20city%20of%20Beit%20Lahiya%2C%20Palestinians%20wade%20through%20the%20rubble%2C%20searching%20for%20corpses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20sound%20of%20one%20of%20them%20sobbing%20breaks%20out%20while%20he%20wraps%20a%20body%20to%20prepare%20for%20burial.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMahmud%20Assaf%2C%2050%2C%20came%20to%20the%20hospital%20from%20Jabalia%20with%20a%20cart%20to%20recover%20two%20of%20his%20relatives'%20children%20who%20had%20been%20patients%20at%20the%20facility%20for%2010%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20found%20Hadi%20paralysed...%20lying%20on%20his%20back%20under%20the%20chairs.%20Everything%20was%20on%20top%20of%20him%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20speaking%20about%20one%20of%20the%20children%20who%20appeared%20barely%20conscious%20and%20severely%20burned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Hamas-run%20health%20ministry%20reported%20on%20December%2012%20that%20the%20Israeli%20army%20forcibly%20entered%20the%20Kamal%20Adwan%20hospital%20in%20Gaza%20City%20during%20a%20%26quot%3Bsiege%26quot%3B%20that%20lasted%20several%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Saturday%2C%20Israel's%20army%20said%20it%20%26quot%3Bcompleted%20its%20activity%20in%20the%20area%20of%20the%20Kamal%20Adwan%20hospital%26quot%3B%2C%20which%20it%20charged%20%26quot%3Bhad%20been%20used%20by%20Hamas%20as%20a%20command%20and%20control%20centre%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20army%20said%20it%20had%20found%20weapons%20and%20arrested%20around%2080%20Hamas%20members%20at%20the%20facility%20--%20the%20last%20functioning%20government%20hospital%20in%20northern%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAssaf%20said%20he%20wanted%20to%20take%20away%20the%20children%20quickly%20now%20that%20the%20army%20had%20withdrawn%2C%20but%20was%20shocked%20by%20the%20%26quot%3Bmassive%2C%20indescribable%20destruction%26quot%3B%20he%20found%20at%20the%20hospital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPatients%20are%20everywhere.%20There%20is%20nothing%20left%20fit%20for%20life%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B(The%20children%20have)%20cases%20of%20serious%20burns%20without%20having%20received%20anything%20to%20eat%2C%20drink%2C%20or%20treatment%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20army%20said%20it%20had%20%26quot%3Bquestioned%20hospital%20workers%26quot%3B%20who%20had%20%26quot%3Bconfessed%20that%20weapons%20were%20hidden%20in%20incubators...%20that%20were%20supposed%20to%20be%20used%20to%20treat%20premature%20babies%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHamas%20accused%20Israel%20of%20carrying%20out%20a%20%26quot%3Bhorrific%20massacre%26quot%3B%20at%20the%20hospital%2C%20claiming%20Israeli%20forces%20%26quot%3Bfired%20at%20patient%20rooms%26quot%3B%2C%20arrested%20staff%2C%20and%20destroyed%20tents%20of%20displaced%20people%20with%20bulldozers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20courtyard%20in%20Kamal%20Adwan%20is%20full%20of%20the%20clearly%20visible%20tracks%20of%20Israeli%20tanks%20and%20bulldozers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20health%20infrastructure%20in%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%20has%20been%20hard%20hit%20by%20aerial%20bombardments%20and%20ground%20operations%20carried%20out%20by%20the%20Israeli%20army%20in%20retaliation%20for%20the%20unprecedented%20October%207%20attack%20by%20Hamas%20on%20Israeli%20territory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20attack%20killed%201%2C139%20people%2C%20mostly%20civilians%2C%20with%20Hamas%20militants%20taking%20about%20250%20hostages%2C%20of%20whom%20105%20have%20been%20released%20and%20several%20killed%2C%20according%20to%20the%20latest%20Israeli%20figures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVowing%20to%20eliminate%20Hamas%2C%20Israel%20has%20carried%20out%20a%20relentless%20bombardment%20of%20Gaza%2C%20alongside%20a%20ground%20invasion%2C%20that%20has%20killed%20more%20than%2018%2C800%20people%2C%20mostly%20women%20and%20children%2C%20