0Over%20University%20Poster%20Row%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EKerala%20Governor%20Arif%20Mohammed%20Khan%20has%20taken%20serious%20note%20of%20the%20action%20of%20the%20State%20Police%2C%20on%20the%20direction%20of%20the%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20in%20placing%20posters%20defamatory%20to%20the%20Governor%20in%20the%20campus%20of%20Calicut%20University.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20black%20banners%20and%20posters%20have%20been%20placed%20inside%20the%20campus%2C%20just%20outside%20the%20University%20Guest%20House%20where%20the%20Governor%20is%20staying%2C%20Kerala%20Raj%20Bhavan%20released%20the%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20governor%20feels%20that%20this%20cannot%20happen%20without%20the%20direction%20of%20the%20chief%20minister%20and%20that%20this%20clearly%20is%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20collapse%20of%20the%20constitutional%20machinery%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20such%20deliberate%20actions%20of%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20precipitate%20the%20breakdown%20of%20constitutional%20machinery.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EComing%20down%20heavily%20on%20Kerala%20Governor%20Arif%20Mohammad%20Khan%2C%20Chief%20Minister%20Pinarayi%20Vijayan%20on%20Sunday%20accused%20him%20of%20attempting%20to%20disrupt%20the%20peaceful%20ambience%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20reporters%2C%20Mr%20Vijayan%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BArif%20Mohammad%20Khan%20is%20making%20a%20move%20to%20destroy%20the%20peaceful%20ambience%20of%20Kerala.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20facing%20a%20black-flag%20protest%20from%20members%20of%20the%20SFI%2C%20the%20students'%20wing%20of%20the%20ruling%20CPI(M)%2C%20the%20Governor%20claimed%20an%20attempt%20on%20his%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20chief%20minister%20said%20the%20governor's%20actions%20were%20such%20that%20they%20sparked%20protests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Vijayan%20further%20highlighted%20the%20comments%20made%20by%20former%20Supreme%20Court%20justice%20Rohinton%20Nariman%20in%20a%20public%20event%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20outlining%20the%20%26quot%3Bwholesale%20reference%20to%20the%20President%2C%26quot%3B%20of%20Bills%20by%20the%20Kerala%20governor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Vijayan%20further%20accused%20the%20governor%20of%20allegedly%20accepting%20proposals%20from%20the%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%20(RSS)%2C%20which%2C%20according%20to%20him%2C%20resulted%20in%20the%20student%20protests.%20The%20chief%20minister%20opposed%20his%20actions%2C%20calling%20them%20%26quot%3Btotally%20wrong.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlso%20drawing%20attention%20to%20the%20Governor's%20choice%20of%20words%2C%20Mr%20Vijayan%20questioned%20how%20he%20could%20use%20such%20harsh%20language.%20He%20also%20expressed%20concern%20over%20the%20Governor's%20approach%20towards%20individuals%2C%20who%20showed%20him%20black%20flags.%20He%20termed%20the%20action%20as%20'provocative'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20SFI%20(Students%20Federation%20of%20India)%2C%20the%20student%20wing%20of%20the%20ruling%20Communist%20Party%20of%20India%20(Marxist)%2C%20staged%20a%20black-flag%20protest%20march%20to%20Calicut%20University%2C%20ahead%20of%20the%20Governor's%20arrival%20on%20campus.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBlack%20banners%20and%20posters%20were%20put%20up%20outside%20Calicut%20University%20Guest%20House%20where%20the%20Governor%20was%20staying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20protesters%20were%2C%20however%2C%20removed%20from%20the%20spot%20by%20the%20police%20on%20the%20instruction%20of%20the%20Governor's%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20statement%20from%20Raj%20Bhavan%20mentioned%20that%20the%20Governor%20took%20serious%20note%20of%20the%20action%20of%20the%20state%20police%2C%20on%20the%20direction%20of%20the%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20in%20placing%20posters%20defamatory%20to%20him%20on%20the%20campus%20of%20Calicut%20University.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Governor%20earlier%20claimed%20that%20the%20police%20were%20prevented%20from%20acting%20against%20'criminals'.%20He%20also%20accused%20Chief%20Minister%20Vijayan%20of%20hatching%20a%20conspiracy%20to%20harm%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20not%20a%20question%20of%20my%20comment%2C%20as%20I%20said%20in%20the%20morning.%20It%20is%20about%20law.%20We%20are%20a%20democratic%20republic%20and%20the%20law%20must%20prevail.%20The%20police%20stood%20like%20silent%20bystanders%20while%20the%20protesters%20were%20at%20it.%20It%20was%20because%20of%20political%20reasons%20that%20they%20stood%20by%20idly.%20My%20car%20was%20surrounded%20and%20the%20protesters%20banged%20on%20it%20with%20all%20the%20force%20that%20they%20could%20muster%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Governor%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20he%20was%20not%20scared%20of%20anyone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDue%20to%20political%20reasons%2C%20the%20Kerala%20Police%20were%20prevented%20from%20acting%20against%20these%20rowdies%20and%20criminals.%20I%20believe%20in%20facing%20up%20to%20brutes.%20I%20am%20not%20scared%20of%20anyone%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702836840000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Fpo4ocme8_kerala-governor_625x300_30_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpinarayi-vijayan-vs-kerala-governor-over-calicut-university-poster-row-black-flags-sfi-protest-4692683%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Kerala%20Governor%20Arif%20Mohammed%20Khan%20has%20taken%20serious%20note%20of%20the%20action%20of%20the%20State%20Police%2C%20on%20the%20direction%20of%20the%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20in%20placing%20posters%20defamatory%20to%20the%20Governor%20in%20the%20campus%20of%20Calicut%20University.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpinarayi-vijayan-vs-kerala-governo