l-Mandeb%20Strait.%3Cp%3EGallo%20Images%2FOrbital%20Horizon%2FCopernicus%20Sentinel%20Data%202021%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Red%20Sea%20is%20one%20of%20the%20world's%20most%20important%20shipping%20routes%20for%20oil%20and%20gas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20at%20its%20narrow%20southern%20end%2C%20commercial%20ships%20must%20pass%20through%20the%20Bab%20el-Mandeb%20Strait%20and%20along%20the%20coast%20of%20Yemen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20ongoing%20attacks%20have%20led%20to%20concerns%20that%20shipments%20of%20oil%2C%20grain%2C%20and%20consumer%20goods%20could%20be%20delayed%20by%20weeks%2C%20while%20shipping%20companies%20are%20also%20faced%20with%20soaring%20insurance%20costs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDavid%20Osler%2C%20an%20insurance%20editor%20for%20Lloyd's%20List%20Intelligence%2C%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Farticle%2Fred-sea-yemen-houthis-attack-ships-f67d941c260528ac40315ecab4c34ca3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Associated%20Press%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20insurance%20costs%20had%20doubled%20for%20vessels%20passing%20through%20the%20Red%20Sea%2C%20and%20that%20the%20most%20expensive%20ships%20could%20have%20to%20pay%20hundreds%20of%20thousands%20of%20dollars%20more%20per%20journey.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmore-big-shipping-companies-suspend-red-sea-operations-2023-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702835552000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F657f10b050edbc52a8651582%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmore-big-shipping-companies-suspend-red-sea-operations-2023-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Houthi%20rebels%20are%20%26quot%3Bdriven%20by%20domestic%20political%20calculations%20in%20Yemen%2C%20regional%20cooperation%20with%20Iran%20and%20an%20ideological%20disposition%20against%20Israel%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20analyst%20wrote.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22pthompson%40insider.com%20(Polly%20Thompson)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A42%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmore-big-shipping-companies-suspend-red-sea-operations-2023-12%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Hamas%20Must%20Review%20All%20Its%20Policies%20Once%20War%20Ends%3A%20Top%20Palestinian%20Official%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EImmediately%20after%20Israel's%20war%20in%20Gaza%20ends%2C%20all%20Palestinian%20factions%20including%20Hamas%20must%20take%20a%20serious%20look%20at%20the%20failure%20of%20their%20policies%20to%20achieve%20freedom%20for%20their%20people%2C%20a%20top%20Palestinian%20Authority%20official%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHussein%20al-Sheikh%2C%2063%2C%20said%20war%20in%20Gaza%20after%20the%20Oct.%207%20attacks%20on%20southern%20Israel%20meant%20Hamas%20should%20make%20a%20%26quot%3Bserious%20and%20honest%20assessment%20and%20reconsider%20all%20its%20policies%20and%20all%20its%20methods%26quot%3B%20once%20fighting%20subsides.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHamas'%20attacks%20killed%201%2C200%20Israelis%2C%20triggering%20a%20relentless%20bombardment%20and%20ground%20war%20that%20has%20killed%20at%20least%2019%2C000%20Palestinians%2C%20displaced%20hundreds%20of%20thousands%20and%20left%20much%20of%20the%20enclave%20in%20ruins.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHussein%20al-Sheikh%2C%20the%20general%20secretary%20of%20President%20Mahmoud%20Abbas's%20Palestinian%20Liberation%20Organization%2C%20is%20seen%20by%20some%20as%20a%20potential%20successor.%20His%20comments%20were%20the%20first%20time%20a%20senior%20PLO%20leader%20has%20talked%20publicly%20about%20Hamas%20tactics%20since%20the%20Oct.%207%20attacks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHussein%20al-Sheikh%20also%20acknowledged%20the%20political%20path%20under%20Oslo%20peace%20accords%20was%20faltering%20and%20as%20it%20currently%20stands%20would%20not%20achieve%20the%20ambition%20of%20the%20Palestinian%20people%20for%20the%20establishment%20of%20a%20Palestinian%20state%20within%20pre-1967%20borders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHussein%20al-Sheikh%20and%20Abbas%20met%20senior%20White%20House%20aide%20Jake%20Sullivan%20in%20Ramallah%20on%20Friday.%20The%20Palestinians%20told%20him%20a%20new%20international%20effort%20was%20needed%20to%20persuade%20Israel%20of%20a%20comprehensive%20solution%20that%20includes%20the%20West%20Bank%2C%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%20and%20East%20Jerusalem%2C%20Hussein%20al-Sheikh%20told%20Reuters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20must%20be%20a%20single%20Palestinian%20government%20governing%20the%20Palestinian%20homeland%2C%26quot%3B%20Hussein%20al-Sheikh%20told%20Reuters%20on%20Saturday%20in%20a%20rare%20interview%20in%20sleek%20offices%20adorned%20with%20portraits%20Abbas%20and%20his%20predecessor%20Yasser%20Arafat%20in%20the%20occupied%20West%20Bank%20city%20of%20Ramallah.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20West%20Bank%20is%20divided%20by%20an%20Israeli%20wall%20and%20fence%20that%20snakes%20hundreds%20of%20miles%20across%20the%20hills.%20Jewish%20settlers%2C%20many%20of%20whom%20cite%20Biblical%20ties%20to%20the%20land%2C%20have%20in%20recent%20years%20expanded%20construction%20in%20areas%20that%20would%20become%20a%20future%20Palestinian%20state.%20Most%20countries%20deem%20Jewish%20settlements%20built%20on%20land%20Israel%20seized%20in%20the%201967%20Middle%20East%20war%20as%20illegal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20offering%20welcome%20verbal%20backing%20for%20a%20Palestinian%20state%20in%20the%20meetings%2C%20Hussein%20al-Sheikh%20said%2C%20Washington%20had%20not%20proposed%20concrete%20mechanisms%20or%20political%20initiatives.%20He%20reiterated%20a%20call%20by%20Abbas%20for%20an%20international%20peace%20conference%20to%20forge%20a%20new%20route.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20senior%20U.S.%20official%20said%20this%20week%20the%20idea%20of%20a%20conference%20had%20been%20discussed%20with%20partners%2C%20but%20the%20proposal%20was%20still%20at%20a%20preliminary%20stage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELEGITIMATE%20REPRESENTATIVE%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EU.S.%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20has%20sent%20a%20series%20of%20top%20officials%20to%20the%20West%20Bank%20to%20meet%20Abbas%20and%20Hussein%20al-Sheikh%2C%20seeking%20to%20revamp%20the%20moribund%20Palestinian%20Authority%20to%20take%20charge%20of%20Gaza%20once%20the%20war%20is%20over%20and%20unify%20the%20administration%20of%20the%20enclave%20and%20the%20West%20Bank.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVisiting%20U.S.%20officials%20have%20discussed%20the%20need%20for%20reforms%20to%20combat%20corruption%2C%20hand%20over%20broader%20executive%20powers%20to%20the%20prime%20minister%20and%20introduce%20new%20blood%20into%20the%20Palestinian%20Authority.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20U.S.%20efforts%2C%20Israeli%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%20said%20on%20Friday%20that%20he%20would%20not%20allow%20the%20Palestinian%20Authority%20to%20run%20Gaza%20after%20the%20war%20and%20suggested%20Israel%20would%20occupy%20it%20instead.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHussein%20al-Sheikh%20said%20the%20Palestinian%20Authority%20was%20the%20legitimate%20representative%20of%20the%20Palestinian%20people%20and%20would%20be%20ready%20to%20take%20control%20of%20Gaza%20after%20the%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20he%20recognised%20that%20the%20unpopular%20Palestinian%20Authority%2C%20which%20many%20Palestinians%20see%20as%20corrupt%2C%20undemocratic%20and%20out%20of%20touch%2C%20needed%20to%20reassess%20its%20role.%20Hamas%20by%20contrast%20has%20grown%20in%20popularity%20since%20the%20attacks%2C%20both%20in%20Gaza%20and%20the%20West%20Bank%2C%20a%20Palestinian%20poll%20showed%20this%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReferring%20to%20Hamas%2C%20which%20has%20fought%20five%20wars%20against%20Israel%20since%202008%2C%20Hussein%20al-Sheikh%20said%20%26quot%3Bit%20is%20not%20acceptable%20for%20some%20to%20believe%20that%20their%20method%20and%20approach%20in%20managing%20the%20conflict%20with%20Israel%20was%20the%20ideal%20and%20the%20best.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAfter%20all%20this%20(killing)%20and%20after%20everything%20that's%20happening%2C%20isn't%20it%20worth%20making%20a%20serious%2C%20honest%20and%20responsible%20assessment%20to%20protect%20our%20people%20and%20our%20Palestinian%20cause%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIsn't%20it%20worth%20discussing%20how%20to%20manage%20this%20conflict%20with%20the%20Israeli%20occupation%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHussein%20al-Sheikh%20said%2060%25%20of%20Gaza%20was%20destroyed%20and%20it%20would%20cost%20%2440%20billion%20to%20rebuild%20over%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%201993%20Oslo%20peace%20accords%20with%20Israel%20were%20partially%20successful%2C%20he%20said%2C%20in%20that%20they%20gave%20Palestinians%20an%20identity%20and%20led%20to%20the%20repatriation%20of%20two%20million%20refugees%20to%20the%20West%20Bank%20and%20Gaza%20from%20countries%20they%20fled%20to%20during%20the%201948%20and%201967%20wars%20with%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20PA%20has%20been%20weakened%20by%20Israel's%20military%20raids%20and%20expansion%20of%20settlements.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbbas%20promoted%20Hussein%20al-Sheikh%20last%20year.%20His%20new%20role%20effectively%20makes%20him%20the%20second%20most%20powerful%20man%20in%20the%20PLO%2C%20an%20umbrella%20for%20non-Islamist%20Palestinian%20factions%20that%20does%20not%20include%20Hamas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20is%20deeply%20unpopular%20among%20Palestinians%20partly%20thanks%20to%20his%20liaison%20role%20with%20the%20occupying%20Israeli%20military.%20Opinion%20polls%20give%20him%20about%203%25%20support.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%2C%20Hamas%20official%20Sami%20Abu%20Zuhri%20said%20Hussein%20al-Sheikh%20was%20%26quot%3Bon%20the%20side%20of%20the%20Israeli%20civil%20administration%2C%20and%20him%20attacking%20the%20Palestinian%20resistance%20isn't%20surprising%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHussein%20al-Sheikh%20said%20it%20was%20his%20job%20to%20work%20with%20Israel%20to%20reduce%20the%20suffering%20of%20Palestinians.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702835520000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Faehhcg08_hamas-reuters-_625x300_14_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisrael-gaza-hamas-palestine-hamas-must-review-all-its-policies-once-war-ends-top-palestinian-official-4692645%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Immediately%20after%20Israel's%20war%20in%20Gaza%20ends%2C%20all%20Palestinian%20factions%20including%20Hamas%20must%20take%20a%20serious%20look%20at%20the%20failure%20of%20their%20policies%20to%20achieve%20freedom%20for%20their%20people%2C%20a%20top%20Palestinian%20Authority%20official%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisrael-gaza-hamas-palestine-hamas-must-review-all-its-policies-once-war-ends-top-palestinian-official-4692645%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisrael-gaza-hamas-palestine-hamas-must-review-all-its-policies-once-war-ends-top-palestinian-official-4692645%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisrael-gaza-hamas-palestine-hamas-must-review-all-its-policies-once-war-ends-top-palestinian-official-4692645%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Inbar%20Haiman%2C%2027-Year-Old%20Israeli%20Woman%20Kidnapped%20By%20Hamas%2C%20Confirmed%20Dead%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%20data-is%3D%5C%22component-paragraph%5C%22%3EA%2027-year-old%20Israeli%20woman%20who%20was%20kidnapped%20from%20the%20Supernova%20music%20festival%20by%20Hamas%20on%20October%207%20has%20been%20confirmed%20dead%2C%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.timesofisrael.com%2Fhostage-inbar-haiman-27-murdered-in-hamas-captivity-officials-say%2F%5C%22%3ETimes%20of%20Israel%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%C2%A0The%20family%20of%20Inbar%20Haiman%20has%20received%20confirmation%20from%20the%20Israel%20Defense%20Forces%20that%20she%20was%20murdered%20in%20captivity%20by%20Hamas%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgettingthemback%2Fposts%2Fpfbid0263dJaj5pC4eJ1obqZ8q4j8ixuEFYi2q88Xt4cAN91LDjn2PSEac6N54ns4uc9LeBl%5C%22%3EHostage%20and%20Missing%20Families%20Forum%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20on%20Saturday.%20The%20statement%20did%20not%20indicate%20how%20or%20when%20Ms%20Haiman%20died.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20data-is%3D%5C%22component-paragraph%5C%22%3E''A%20gifted%20girl%2C%20full%20of%20love%20with%20endless%20giving.%20Creative%20girl%20and%20full%20of%20joy%20of%20life%2C''%20the%20forum%20wrote%20on%20Facebook%20while%20describing%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20data-is%3D%5C%22component-paragraph%5C%22%3E''Inbar%20was%20an%20avid%20art%20enthusiast%20and%20graffiti%20artist.%20She%20had%20also%20studied%20filmmaking%20in%20high%20school.%20She%20was%20a%20fan%20of%20Maccabi%20Haifa%20soccer%20team.%20She%20met%20her%20partner%20Noam%20Alon%20almost%20two%20years%20ago%20while%20studying%20Visual%20Communication%20at%20the%20Wizo%20Academic%20Center%20in%20Haifa.%20This%20month%20they%20were%20supposed%20to%20have%20started%20their%20fourth%20year%20of%20studies%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20forum%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20data-is%3D%5C%22component-paragraph%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ESee%20the%20post%20here%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fplugins%2Fpost.php%3Fhref%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.facebook.com%252Fgettingthemback%252Fposts%252Fpfbid0222b6utFWziSprw2ozBpZ4E9SUbi3qngJMrJQ8S8ASgX8DiDYyyNs7cdiTN58BG4l%26show_text%3Dtrue%26width%3D500%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22250%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20data-is%3D%5C%22component-paragraph%5C%22%3EThe%2027-year-old%2C%20a%20visual%20communications%20student%20from%20Haifa%2C%20was%20abducted%20from%20the%20Nova%20music%20festival%2C%20which%20was%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20sites%20of%20Hamas%20attack%20on%20October%207.%20Ms%20Haiman%20was%20volunteering%20at%20the%20Supernova%20Music%20Festival%20when%20Hamas%20operatives%20unleashed%20horror%20on%20Israeli%20civilians.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20onslaught%20began%2C%20panic-stricken%20people%20at%20the%20music%20festival%20dashed%20across%20a%20field%20towards%20their%20vehicles%2C%20to%20the%20sound%20of%20gunshots%20in%20the%20background.%20The%2027-year-old%20woman%20also%20ran%20for%20her%20life%20but%20was%20caught%20by%20a%20Hamas%20operative%2C%20while%20her%20two%20friends%20managed%20to%20escape.%C2%A0In%20a%20video%20that%20later%20went%20viral%2C%20Ms%20Haiman%20was%20seen%20being%20dragged%20by%20two%20Hamas%20operatives%20on%20motorbikes.%20After%20her%20capture%2C%20her%20boyfriend%20Noam%20Alon%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhamas-attack-israel-gaza-war-palestine-iran-hezbollah-keep-her-alive-israeli-hostages-boyfriend-pleads-for-her-release-4504002%5C%22%3E%20pleaded%20with%20the%20authorities%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20her%20safe%20return.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUnfortunately%20two%20terrorists%20on%20motorbikes%20came%20right%20at%20that%20moment%20and%20they%20grabbed%20Inbar%20and%20took%20her%20to%20Gaza.%20All%20I'm%20asking%20is%20for%20them%20to%20be%20as%20kind%20as%20possible%20and%20keep%20her%20alive%20-%20not%20expecting%20too%20much%20-%20just%20for%20them%20to%20be%20human%2C%20and%20for%20them%20to%20give%20the%20hostages%20food%20and%20water%20and%20medical%20%5Battention%5D%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Alon%2C%20told%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthemessenger.com%2Fnews%2Fisraeli-hostage-inbar-haiman-boyfriend-hamas-terror-attack-music-festival%5C%22%3EThe%20Messenger%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20an%