ident%20Jagdeep%20Dhankhar%20on%20Sunday%20described%20%26quot%3Banti-national%20narratives%26quot%3B%20as%20the%20Covid%20virus%20and%20said%20they%20have%20to%20be%20neutralised.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20speaking%20as%20chief%20guest%20at%20the%20inaugural%20function%20of%208th%20three-day%20international%20seminar%20on%20'Vasudhaiv%20Kutumbakam%3A%20Shrimad%20Bhagwadgita%20%26amp%3B%20Global%20Unity'%20organised%20by%20Kurukshetra%20University%20and%20Kurukshetra%20Development%20Board.%20The%20event%20was%20organised%20here%20as%20part%20of%20the%20ongoing%20International%20Gita%20Festival.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDhankhar%20said%20either%20in%20a%20planned%20way%20or%20due%20to%20lack%20of%20understanding%2C%20a%20few%20people%20%26quot%3Btake%20pleasure%20in%20floating%20anti-national%20narratives%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20should%20not%20happen.%20You%20should%20oppose%20it%20(such%20narratives).%20It%20is%20like%20Covid%20virus%20that%20has%20to%20be%20neutralised%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaryana%20Chief%20Minister%20Manohar%20Lal%20Khattar%2C%20Gita%20Manishi%20Swami%20Gyananand%2C%20and%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20Sudhanshu%20Trivedi%20were%20also%20present%20at%20the%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20philosophy%20of%20Gita%20is%20the%20bedrock%20of%20Indian%20civilisation%2C%20its%20culture%20and%20in%20the%20present%20times%20the%20soul%20of%20India's%20governance%20with%20an%20emphasis%20on%20objectivity%2C%20transparency%2C%20equity%20and%20commitment%20to%20universal%20brotherhood%2C%20said%20the%20vice%20president.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20today%20India%20is%20making%20rapid%20progress%20in%20varied%20fields.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B..We%20are%20a%20world%20power%2C%20we%20stand%20for%20peace%2C%20we%20stand%20for%20global%20stability.%20We%20want%20to%20take%20our%20Bharat%20in%202047%20at%20peak%20when%20we%20will%20be%20into%20centenary%20celebration%20of%20our%20Independence%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReferring%20to%20the%20Russia-Ukraine%20and%20Israel-Hamas%20conflict%2C%20Dhankhar%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BAfter%20the%20World%20War%20II%2C%20the%20world%20has%20not%20seen%20this%20much%20pain%20as%20it%20is%20seeing%20today.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20virtually%20sitting%20on%20a%20volcano.%20World's%20two%20'configurations'%20--%20one%20Israel-Hamas%20and%20another%20Ukraine-Russia%20--%20are%20well%20known%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20while%20adding%20Gita's%20philosophy%20is%20as%20relevant%20today%20as%20never%20before.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20India's%20Prime%20Minister%20has%20made%20two%20historic%20statements%20in%20the%20past.%20First%20one%20was%20nearly%20one-and-a-half%20years%20back%20that%20'we%20are%20not%20living%20in%20an%20era%20of%20expansion'.%20In%20saying%20so%2C%20the%20PM%20took%20pride%20this%20country%20never%20in%20its%20history%20has%20thought%20of%20expansion.%20We%20have%20suffered%20invasions%2C%20incursions%20of%20all%20kinds%2C%20but%20we%20have%20never%20believed%20in%20expansion%20policy%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20there%20were%20two%20big%20issues%20before%20the%20world%2C%20PM%20Modi%20taking%20guidance%20from%20the%20Gita%20said%20that%20every%20possible%20effort%20should%20be%20made%20to%20avoid%20war%2C%20through%20dialogue%20and%20diplomacy%2C%20Dhankhar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMaking%20a%20reference%20to%20the%20Mahabharat%20era%2C%20he%20said%20no%20effort%20was%20spared%20by%20Lord%20Krishna%20to%20ensure%20that%20there%20be%20no%20war.%20%26quot%3BBut%20once%20this%20becomes%20inevitable%2C%20even%20then%20Lord%20Krishna%20gave%20'gyan'%20to%20Arjuna%20which%20we%20need%20to%20ponder%20upon%20today%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELord%20Krishna%20told%20Arjuna%20never%20to%20leave%20path%20of%20duty...and%20%26quot%3Btoday%20PM%20Modi%20is%20doing%20so%26quot%3B%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDhankhar%20also%20praised%20Chief%20Minister%20Khattar%20and%20described%20him%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Btrue%20follower%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20Gita.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20vice%20president%20said%20that%20while%20Khattar's%20identity%20as%20a%20chief%20minister%20is%20endearing%20to%20the%20people%2C%20he%20is%20known%20for%20transparency%2C%20fairness%20and%20accountability.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20on%20the%20occasion%2C%20Khattar%20said%20the%20Gita%20is%20not%20just%20a%20book%20or%20scripture%2C%20it%20is%20the%20%26quot%3Bessence%20of%20life%2C%20Gita%20is%20universal%20and%20eternal%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDhankhar%20emphasized%20the%20alignment%20of%20the%20Central%20government%20with%20the%20principles%20of%20%26quot%3BGita%20governance%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20applauded%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi's%20commitment%20to%20righteousness%20and%20duty%2C%20citing%20the%20importance%20of%20performing%20duties%20without%20attachment%20to%20the%20results%2C%20as%20advocated%20in%20the%20Gita.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDhankhar%20said%20the%20fundamental%20of%20democracy%20is%20that%20all%20are%20equal%20before%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEarlier%20some%20people%20thought%20they%20are%20above%20law.%20But%20a%20big%20change%20happened%20and%20today%20no%20one%20is%20outside%20the%20ambit%20of%20law%2C%20this%20is%20the%20ground%20reality.%20I%20can%20assure%20you%20to%20achieve%20this%20is%20not%20easy.%20It%20was%20a%20formidable%20challenge%2C%20challenge%20from%20those%20who%20were%20established%2C%20those%20who%20had%20a%20great%20support%20system%20--%20in%20the%20system%20and%20outside.%20But%20today%20we%20can%20hold%20our%20head%20high%20and%20say%20Gita%20governance%20is%20there%20and%20all%20are%20equal%20before%20law%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWithout%20naming%20anyone%2C%20the%20vice%20president%20said%20if%20one%20gets%20notice%20as%20per%20law%2C%20the%20procedure%20under%20law%20should%20be%20followed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20new%20culture%20that%20%26quot%3Bwe%20will%20take%20to%20roads%20if%20we%20get%20notice%20as%20per%20law%26quot%3B%20is%20not%20what%20Gita%20taught%20us%2C%20he%20asserted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDhankhar%2C%20along%20with%20his%20wife%20Sudesh%20Dhankhar%2C%20also%20visited%20the%20Assam%20Pavilion%20at%20the%20event%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20India%20is%20poised%20to%20be%20the%20third%20largest%20economy%20in%20the%20world%20by%202030.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDhankhar%20also%20said%20that%20the%20Gita%20gives%20%26quot%3Bsolutions%20to%20all%20problems%20and%20teaches%20us%20inclusivity%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20urged%20every%20citizen%20to%20contribute%20to%20India's%20development%2C%20terming%20'Amrit%20Kaal'%20as%20the%20%26quot%3Bgolden%20era%26quot%3B%20for%20the%20country%2C%20and%20set%20a%20goal%20to%20transform%20India%20into%20a%20developed%20nation%20by%202047.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702834140000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Faamc94kg_jagdeep-dhankhar_625x300_17_December_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fanti-national-narratives-like-covid-must-be-neutralised-vice-president-4692450%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Vice%20President%20Jagdeep%20Dhankhar%20on%20Sunday%20described%20%26quot%3Banti-national%20narratives%26quot%3B%20as%20the%20Covid%20virus%20and%20said%20they%20have%20to%20be%20neutralised.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fanti-national-narratives-like-covid-must-be-neutralised-vice-president-4692450%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fanti-national-narratives-like-covid-must-be-neutralised-vice-president-4692450%2Famp%2