0our%20digital%20data%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20That%20includes%20the%20codes%20that%20encrypt%20data%20across%20our%20public%20networks%20and%20protect%20information%20in%20places%20like%20banks%2C%20government%20agencies%2C%20and%20major%20companies.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EIt's%20known%20as%20%26quot%3BQ-Day.%26quot%3B%20It'll%20be%20a%20massive%20turning%20point%20for%20how%20the%20world%20thinks%20about%20digital%20privacy%2C%20as%20it%20could%20put%20confidential%20information%20at%20risk%20of%20exposure.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECybersecurity%20experts%20don't%20all%20agree%20on%20when%20this%20day%20will%20arrive.%20Some%20researchers%20predict%20that%20%26quot%3BQ-Day%26quot%3B%20will%20come%20sometime%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20century%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Finvestigates%2Fspecial-report%2Fus-china-tech-quantum%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eaccording%20to%20Reuters%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0Others%20think%20it's%20set%20to%20arrive%20much%20sooner.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BQ-Day%26quot%3B%20might%20come%20by%202025%2C%20Tilo%20Kunz%2C%20the%20executive%20vice%20president%20of%20the%20Canadian%20cybersecurity%20firm%20Quantum%20Defen5e%2C%20told%20officials%20at%20the%20US%20Department%20of%20Defense%2C%20according%20to%20Reuters.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-is-quantum-computing-2013-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EQuantum%20computers%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20vastly%20more%20powerful%20than%20regular%20computers%20as%20they%20rely%20on%20the%20properties%20of%20subatomic%20particles%20to%20do%20some%20serious%20number-crunching.%20They%20can%20perform%20calculations%20that%20wouldn't%20be%20possible%20on%20today's%20computers%20and%20process%20information%20at%20drastically%20higher%20speeds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20major%20issue%20right%20now%20is%20that%20the%20key%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-is-q