20Sharma's%20Form%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Rohit%20had%20an%20impressive%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%2C%20his%20form%20for%20MI%20over%20the%20last%20couple%20of%20years%20wasn't%20the%20best.%20In%20IPL%202022%20season%2C%20he%20scored%20268%20runs%20in%2014%20games%20at%20an%20average%20of%2019.14%20while%20in%20the%202023%20season%20saw%20him%20scoring%20332%20runs%20in%2016%20matches%20at%20an%20average%20of%2020.75.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20it%20can't%20be%20said%20that%20captaincy%20was%20taking%20a%20toll%20on%20Rohit's%20performance%2C%20MI%20did%20not%20to%20make%20a%20big%20change%20if%20they%20are%20to%20challenge%20for%20the%20title%20again%2C%20while%20also%20paving%20the%20way%20for%20the%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIPL%202025%20Mega%20Auction%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20just%20one%20season%20to%20go%20before%20the%20IPL%202025%20mega%20auction%20gets%20underway%2C%20Mumbai%20Indians%20had%20to%20lay%20out%20plans%20for%20the%20future.%20Before%20the%20last%20mega%20auction%2C%20the%20BCCI%20allowed%20franchises%20to%20retain%20a%20maximum%20of%20three%20Indian%20and%202%20overseas%20players.%20The%20complex%20situation%20saw%20them%20release%20Hardik%20but%20the%20franchise%20doesn't%20want%20to%20repeat%20the%20same%20mistakes%20this%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20all%20likeliness%2C%20MI's%20Indian%20retentions%20would%20be%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Suryakumar%20Yadav%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1492-suryakumar-yadav-playerprofile%5C%22%3ESuryakumar%20Yadav%3C%2Fa%3E%20(World%20No.%20T20I%20batter)%2C%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Jasprit%20Bumrah%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1724-jasprit-bumrah-playerprofile%5C%22%3EJasprit%20Bumrah%3C%2Fa%3E%20(arguably%20the%20best%20T20%20bowler%20in%20the%20world)%20and%20skipper%20Hardik%20Pandya.%20While%20the%20exact%20rules%20for%20the%20IPL%202025%20auction%20aren't%20known%20yet%2C%20Rohit%20looks%20like%20a%20big%20candidate%20to%20be%20released%20if%20only%20three%20Indians%20are%20allowed%20to%20be%20retained.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESmooth%20Transition%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20Rohit%20Sharma%2036%20and%20still%20a%20capable%20batter%2C%20Mumbai%20Indians%20want%20to%20make%20the%20captaincy%20change%20at%20a%20time%20where%20the%20Hitman%20can%20oversee%20the%20transition%20and%20help%20Hardik%20become%20an%20even%20better%20leader.%20By%20making%20a%20captaincy%20change%20early%2C%20MI%20are%20reducing%20the%20risk%20of%20finding%20late%20solutions%20to%20the%20problem%20in%20a%20scenario%20where%20Rohit%20might%20no%20longer%20be%20with%20the%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702831980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2F35fc6tdo_rohit-sharma-hardik-pandya_625x300_17_December_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fexplained-what-led-to-mumbai-indians-captain-change-from-rohit-sharma-to-hardik-pandya-4689830%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22After%20leading%20Mumbai%20Indians%20for%2010%20seasons%2C%20Rohit%20Sharma%20was%20replaced%20by%20Hardik%20Pandya%20as%20the%20captain%20of%20the%20franchise%20ahead%20of%20IPL%202024%20season.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fexplained-what-led-to-mumbai-indians-captain-change-from-rohit-sharma-to-hardik-pandya-4689830%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fexplained-what-led-to-mumbai-indians-captain-change-from-rohit-sharma-to-hardik-pandya-4689830%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fexplained-what-led-to-mumbai-indians-captain-change-from-rohit-sharma-to-hardik-pandya-4689830%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Moment%20landslide%20sweeps%20down%20mountainside%20into%20Lake%20Garda%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22