nisters%20of%20yellow%20smoke.%20They%20were%20pinned%20down%20by%20MPs%20who%20were%20in%20the%20House%20during%20the%20Zero%20Hour.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSince%20the%20seriousness%20of%20the%20matter%20lies%20in%20this%20fact%2C%20which%20relates%20to%20our%20own%20security%2C%20members%20of%20the%20Opposition%20are%20duty%20bound%20to%20demand%20an%20explanation%20from%20the%20government%20and%20expect%20corrective%20measures%20to%20be%20taken%20urgently%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Chowdhury%20wrote%20to%20Lok%20Sabha%20Speaker%20Om%20Birla.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20leader%20conceded%20that%20the%20two%20incidents%20(2001%20and%202023%20breach)%20are%20%26quot%3Bworld%20apart%26quot%3B.%20He%20then%20said%20that%20the%20recent%20incident%20has%20also%20%26quot%3Bbrought%20to%20the%20fore%20issues%20relating%20to%20the%20security%20of%20the%20institutions%20which%20are%20the%20core%20of%20our%20democratic%20practices%20and%20ethos%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMembers%20across%20party%20lines%20%26quot%3Bsolidly%26quot%3B%20stood%20as%20one%20when%20LK%20Advani%20made%20a%20detailed%20statement%20following%20the%202001%20attack%2C%20underlined%20the%20Congress%20leader%2C%20adding%20that%20Sonia%20Gandhi%2C%20the%20then%20Congress%20president%2C%20called%20on%20then%20Prime%20Minister%20AB%20Vajpayee%20and%20his%20deputy%2C%20LK%20Advani%2C%20to%20enquire%20about%20their%20well-being.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20present%20instance%20too%2C%20it%20is%20but%20appropriate%20for%20the%20Home%20Minister%20to%20make%20a%20Statement%20in%20the%20House%20on%20the%20incident%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Chowdhury%2C%20the%20leader%20of%20the%20Congress%20party%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20Om%20Birla%2C%20in%20a%20letter%20to%20all%20MPs%2C%20said%20that%20he%20has%20constituted%20a%20%26quot%3Bhigh-powered%20committee%26quot%3B%20to%20review%20all%20aspects%20of%20security%20in%20the%20Parliament%20complex%20and%20formulate%20a%20concrete%20action%20plan%20to%20ensure%20that%20such%20incidents%20do%20not%20recur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20opposition%20parties%20seeking%20a%20statement%20from%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20and%20some%20even%20demanding%20his%20resignation%2C%20Mr%20Birla%20has%20said%20that%20security%20in%20the%20Parliament%20House%20Estate%20comes%20under%20the%20jurisdiction%20of%20parliament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Chowdhury%20also%20stressed%20that%20%26quot%3Bprotocols%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bprocedures%26quot%3B%20for%20issuing%20and%20regulating%20entry%20of%20visitors%20to%20witness%20the%20proceedings%20of%20the%20House%20must%20be%20looked%20into%20as%20well%20to%20avoid%20a%20repeat%20of%20such%20incidents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20total%20of%2013%20MPs%20were%20suspended%20from%20parliament%20on%20Thursday%20%26quot%3Bfor%20creating%20a%20ruckus%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20House%20over%20their%20demand%20for%20a%20statement%20on%20the%20breach.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%2013%20MPs%20suspended%20from%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20nine%20are%20from%20the%20Congress%2C%20two%20from%20the%20CPM%2C%20one%20from%20the%20CPI%2C%20and%20one%20from%20the%20DMK.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BConsidering%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20Members%20who%20have%20been%20suspended%20on%20account%20of%20%26quot%3Bunruly%20conduct%26quot%3B%20were%20pressing%20for%20an%20explanation%20from%20the%20government%20on%20very%20troubling%20issues%2C%20to%20me%2C%20it%20appears%20to%20be%20appropriate%20to%20hear%20them%20on%20their%20concerns%20and%20points%20of%20view%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Chowdhury.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Saturday%2C%20Om%20Birla%20asserted%20that%20there%20is%20no%20connection%20between%20the%20security%20breach%20and%20the%20suspension%20of%2013%20MPs%20from%20the%20Lower%20House.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20unwarranted.%20There%20is%20no%20association%20between%20the%20suspension%20of%20honourable%20members%20and%20the%20incident%20which%20took%20place%20on%20December%2013%2C%202023.%20The%20suspension%20of%20honourable%20members%20is%20purely%20to%20uphold%20the%20sanctity%20of%20the%20house%2C%26quot%3B%20read%20Mr%20Birla's%20letter.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702830060000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2F3hpmuhho_parliament-security-breach-_625x300_13_December_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcongress-cites-lk-advani-seeks-amit-shah-statement-on-parliament-security-breach-4692277%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Following%20the%20parliament%20attack%20on%20December%2013%2C%202001%2C%20LK%20Advani%20made%20a%20statement%20on%20the%20floor%20of%20the%20House%2C%20underscored%20Congress%20leader%20Adhir%20Ranjan%20Chowdhury%2C%20pressing%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20to%20make%20a%20statement%20on%20breach%20in%20parliament%20security.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcongress-cites-lk-advani-seeks-amit-shah-statement-on-parliament-security-breach-4692277%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcongress-cites-lk-advani-seeks-amit-shah-statement-on-parliament-security-breach-4692277%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcongress-cites-lk-advani-seeks-amit-shah-statement-on-parliament-security-breach-4692277%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Timoth%C3%A9e%20Chalamet%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98Wonka%E2%80%99%20Tops%20Box%20Office%20With%20%2439%20Million%20Debut%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702829699000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2FScreen-Shot-2023-12-12-at-11.13.12-AM.png%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D563%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1235842643%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%E2%80%9CWonka%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20fantasy%20musical%20starring%20Timoth%