ays%20Israel%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Israeli%20army%20said%20on%20Sunday%20it%20had%20uncovered%20the%20biggest%20Hamas%20tunnel%20in%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%20so%20far%2C%20just%20a%20few%20hundred%20metres%20from%20a%20key%20border%20crossing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuch%20was%20its%20size%20that%20small%20vehicles%20would%20be%20able%20to%20travel%20within%20the%20tunnel%2C%20an%20AFP%20photographer%20granted%20access%20to%20it%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20underground%20passage%20formed%20part%20of%20a%20wider%20branching%20network%20that%20stretched%20for%20over%20four%20kilometres%20and%20came%20within%20400%20metres%20(1%2C300%20feet)%20of%20the%20Erez%20border%20crossing%2C%20the%20army%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EEXPOSED%3A%20The%20biggest%20Hamas%20terrorist%20tunnel%20discovered.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnThis%20massive%20tunnel%20system%20branches%20out%20and%20spans%20well%20over%20four%20kilometers%20(2.5%20miles).%20Its%20entrance%20is%20located%20only%20400%20meters%20(1%2C310%20feet)%20from%20the%20Erez%20Crossing%E2%80%94used%20by%20Gazans%20on%20a%20daily%20basis%20to%20enter%20Israel%20for%20work%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FRcjK5LbvGL%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FRcjK5LbvGL%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Israel%20Defense%20Forces%20(%40IDF)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FIDF%2Fstatus%2F1736407306311475360%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EDecember%2017%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20cost%20millions%20of%20dollars%20and%20took%20years%20to%20construct%2C%20Israeli%20forces%20said%2C%20with%20the%20project%20lead%20by%20Mohamed%20Yahya%2C%20brother%20of%20Hamas%20chief%20Yahya%20Sinwar%2C%20who%20is%20believed%20to%20have%20masterminded%20the%20October%207%20attacks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20honeycomb%20of%20passageways%20features%20a%20drainage%20systems%2C%20electricity%2C%20ventilation%2C%20sewage%20and%20a%20communication%20network%20as%20well%20as%20rails.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20floor%20is%20compacted%20earth%20while%20its%20walls%20are%20reinforced%20concrete%20and%20its%20entrance%20is%20a%20metal%20cylinder%20with%201.5%20centimetre%20(half-inch)%20thick%20walls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFootage%20released%20by%20the%20Israeli%20army%2C%20which%20it%20said%20was%20filmed%20by%20Hamas%2C%20showed%20a%20small%20construction%20vehicle%20being%20driven%20into%20the%20tunnel%2C%20an%20extensive%20temporary%20warehouse%20filled%20with%20pre-cast%20concrete%20for%20lining%20the%20walls%20and%20workers%20digging%20beneath%20the%20earth%20using%20crude%20power%20tools.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Israeli%20army%20said%20it%20had%20found%20a%20large%20number%20of%20weapons%20stored%20in%20the%20tunnel%2C%20ready%20to%20be%20used%20in%20an%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPeople%2C%20goods%2C%20weapons%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHamas%20had%20expended%20huge%20resources%20in%20the%20project%2C%20said%20Lieutenant%20Colonel%20Richard%20Hecht%2C%20an%20army%20spokesman%2C%20and%20did%20so%20to%20%26quot%3Bserve%20only%20one%20purpose%20--%20attacking%20the%20State%20of%20Israel%20and%20its%20residents%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20tunnel%20was%20deliberately%20built%20near%20the%20Erez%20crossing%2C%20which%20Israel%20uses%20to%20facilitate%20the%20strictly%20controlled%20entry%20of%20Palestinian%20workers%20and%20those%20travelling%20for%20medical%20care.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20Hamas%2C%20attacking%20the%20people%20of%20Israel%20continues%20to%20take%20priority%20over%20supporting%20the%20people%20of%20Gaza%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20group%20launched%20a%20surprise%20attack%20against%20southern%20Israel%20on%20October%207%2C%20killing%20around%201%2C140%20people%2C%20mostly%20civilians%2C%20and%20taking%20about%20250%20hostages%2C%20according%20to%20the%20latest%20Israeli%20figures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%2C%20Israel%20set%20out%20to%20destroy%20Hamas%20and%20launched%20a%20relentless%20bombardment%20and%20ground%20invasion%20of%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%20to%20achieve%20that%20goal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Hamas-run%20health%20ministry%20in%20Gaza%20says%20Israel%20has%20killed%20more%20than%2018%2C800%20people%2C%20mostly%20women%20and%20children%2C%20during%20the%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDubbed%20the%20%26quot%3BGaza%20Metro%26quot%3B%20by%20the%20Israeli%20military%2C%20the%20labyrinth%20of%20tunnels%20beneath%20the%20coastal%20territory%20was%20initially%20devised%20as%20a%20way%20of%20circumventing%20the%20crushing%20Israeli-Egyptian%20blockade%2C%20in%20place%20since%202007.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHundreds%20of%20tunnels%20were%20built%20under%20the%20border%20with%20Egypt%20and%20into%20the%20Sinai%20Desert%2C%20allowing%20people%2C%20goods%20and%20weapons%20to%20cross%20into%20Gaza%20from%20the%20outside%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20the%202014%20war%20with%20Israel%2C%20the%20tunnel%20network%20has%20been%20expanded%20and%20Hamas%20has%20made%20frequent%20use%20of%20it%20to%20facilitate%20its%20rocket%20launches.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20study%20published%20on%20October%2017%20by%20the%20Modern%20War%20Institute%20at%20the%20US%20military%20academy%20West%20Point%20said%20there%20were%201%2C300%20tunnels%20stretching%20over%20500%20kilometres%20(310%20miles).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Israeli%20army%20said%20at%20the%20beginning%20of%20December%20that%20it%20had%20discovered%20more%20than%20800%20tunnels%2C%20with%20500%20destroyed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReports%20in%20Israeli%20media%20last%20week%20said%20that%20the%20army%20was%20considering%20flooding%20the%20tunnels%20with%20seawater%20pumped%20from%20the%20Mediterranean%20and%20had%20already%20conducted%20succesful%20tests.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702828260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fod337ad_israel-hamas-tunnel_625x300_17_December_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fbiggest-hamas-tunnel-with-4-km-long-network-found-under-gaza-says-israel-4692191%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Israeli%20army%20said%20on%20Sunday%20it%20had%20uncovered%20the%20biggest%20Hamas%20tunnel%20in%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%20so%20far%2C%20just%20a%20few%20hundred%20metres%20from%20a%20key%20border%20crossing.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fbiggest-hamas-tunnel-with-4-km-long-network-found-under-gaza-says-israel-4692191%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fbiggest-hamas-tunnel-with-4-km-long-network-found-under-gaza-says-israel-4692191%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fbiggest-hamas-tunnel-with-4-km-long-network-found-under-gaza-says-israel-4692191%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BLost%203%20ODIs%20As%20Captain...%26quot%3B%3A%20Rahul's%20Honest%20Take%20On%20Win%20Over%20SA%20In%201st%20ODI%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFollowing%20his%20side's%20eight-wicket%20win%20over%20South%20Africa%20in%20the%20first%20ODI%2C%20Indian%20skipper%20KL%20Rahul%20said%20that%20it%20was%20finally%20great%20to%20have%20a%20win%20in%20the%20country%20after%20losing%20three%20ODIs%20as%20a%20captain%20last%20year.%20KL's%20men%20took%20a%201-0%20lead%20in%20the%20series%2C%20beating%20South%20Africa%20by%20eight%20wickets%20in%20the%20first%20ODI%20at%20Johannesburg%20on%20Sunday.%20Arshdeep%20Singh's%20five-wicket%20haul%20and%20fifties%20by%20debutant%20Sai%20Sudarshan%20and%20Shreyas%20Iyer%20were%20the%20key%20