s%20party%20was%20blown%20away%20in%20the%20recent%20assembly%20elections%20to%20the%20three%20north%20Indian%20states%20of%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Chhattisgarh%20and%20Rajasthan%20when%2C%20for%20the%20most%20part%2C%20it%20engaged%20the%20BJP%20in%20straight%20fights%2C%20is%20it%20%3Cem%3Efinis%3C%2Fem%3E%20for%20the%20party%20in%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20as%20a%20consequence%2C%20is%20it%20over%20for%20the%20%E2%80%98INDIA%E2%80%99%20alliance%20in%20the%20joust%20for%20power%20at%20the%20Centre%20against%20the%20ruling%20BJP%2C%20since%20the%20Congress%20is%20the%20largest%20component%20of%20the%20bloc%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlso%2C%20a%20related%20question%3A%20Will%20the%20anti-BJP%20forces%20in%20the%20crucial%20north%20Indian%20states%20of%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20or%20Bihar%20be%20able%20to%20successfully%20take%20on%20the%20BJP%20helmed%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20%3Cem%3Ewithout%3C%2Fem%3E%20the%20effective%20and%20absolute%20support%20of%20the%20Congress%2C%20no%20matter%20that%20in%20recent%20decades%20this%20party%20has%20weakened%20considerably%20in%20these%20states%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPut%20another%20way%2C%20are%20the%20pre-eminent%20state%20parties%20of%20UP%20and%20Bihar%20self-sufficient%20in%20tackling%20the%20BJP%20in%20the%20way%20that%20the%20DMK%20is%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%20or%20even%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%20in%20West%20Bengal%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20record%20does%20not%20seem%20to%20suggest%20that.%20Nevertheless%2C%20in%20ordinary%20conversation%20and%20in%20general%20analysis%2C%20it%20is%20all%20too%20commonly%20assumed%20that%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20regional%20opponents%20in%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20are%20strong%20enough%20to%20hold%20their%20own%20against%20the%20BJP%2C%20but%20the%20Congress%20is%20not.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20has%20frequently%20been%20called%20the%20%E2%80%9Cweak%20link%E2%80%9D%2C%20although%20it%20is%20acknowledged%20by%20the%20INDIA%20parties%20that%20there%20cannot%20be%20a%20national%20challenge%20to%20the%20BJP%20by%20keeping%20the%20Congress%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBihar%20chief%20minister%20and%20JD(U)%20founder%20Nitish%20Kumar%20was%20most%20explicit%20about%20this%20when%20he%20broached%20anti-BJP%20parties%20to%20come%20together%20to%20challenge%20Modi%20rule%20before%20the%20alliance%20was%20officially%20announced%20earlier%20this%20year.%20Has%20the%20situation%20changed%20since%20then%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fnitish-kumar-anchor-opposition-unity-challenges%5C%22%3EAs%20the%20Anchor%20of%20Opposition%20Unity%20in%202024%2C%20Nitish%20Kumar%20Faces%20His%20Biggest%20Test%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20looking%20at%20the%20utility%20of%20the%20Congress%20for%20the%20alliance%20in%20UP%20or%20Bihar%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20useful%20to%20consider%20that%20even%20at%20its%20weakest%2C%20the%20party%20has%20summoned%20close%20to%2010%25%20of%20the%20popular%20vote%20in%20a%20parliamentary%20election%20in%20these%20states.%20Though%20usually%20scattered%2C%20this%20vote%20is%20sufficient%20to%20fill%20important%20gaps%20in%20an%20alliance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndeed%2C%20in%20the%202009%20Lok%20Sabha%20poll%2C%20the%20Congress%20pulled%20off%20as%20many%20as%2021%20seats%20in%20UP%2C%20just%20short%20of%20SP%E2%80%99s%2023%20and%20ahead%20of%20the%20BSP%20(20%20seats).%20It%20would%20appear%20that%20while%20long%20past%20its%20finest%20hour%2C%20the%20party%20still%20has%20latent%20votes%20(given%20historical%20associations)%20that%20can%20come%20good%20when%20the%20political%20alchemy%20is%20right.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20we%20look%20at%20the%20overall%20score-line%20in%20the%20recent%20polls%2C%20the%20Congress%20did%20notch%20a%20sensational%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Ftelangana-bharat-rashtra-samithi-congress-kcr%5C%22%3Ewin%20in%20Telangana%3C%2Fa%3E.%20However%2C%20this%20was%20against%20the%20BRS%2C%20a%20regional%20entity%20and%2C%20crucially%2C%20not%20against%20the%20BJP%2C%20which%20has%20formidable%20strengths%20that%20cannot%20be%20overlooked%20in%20any%20assessment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ruling%20dispensation%20at%20the%20Centre%20has%20demonstrated%20ideological%20expansion%2C%20sturdiness%20and%20clarity.%20It%20has%20a%20superb%20organisation%20that%20no%20party%20matches%2C%20and%20massive%20money%20and%20muscle%20power%20on%20account%20of%20its%20control%20over%20every%20organ%20of%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%2C%20it%20has%20the%20unerring%20tendency%20to%20be%20vengeful%20and%20vituperative%20against%20opponents%20and%20dissenters%2C%20and%20in%20untrammelled%20fashion%20uses%20the%20coercive%20apparatus%20of%20the%20state%20against%20them.%20In%20addition%2C%20it%20has%20near-total%20sway%20over%20the%20media%20through%20a%20carrot-and-stick%20policy%20honed%20over%20a%20decade.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20short%20point%20is%2C%20has%20the%20hill%20the%20Congress%20and%20its%20allies%20must%20climb%20become%20higher%20after%20the%20recent%20state%20polls%3F%20Are%20the%20possibilities%20that%20looked%20attainable%20after%20Karnataka%20receding%20in%20the%20mirror%20now%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F15183536%2FBJP-rally-1024x576.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F15183536%2FBJP-rally-1024x576.jpeg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F15183536%2FBJP-rally-300x169.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F15183536%2FBJP-rally.jpeg%201200w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-689365%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22473%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThe%20BJP%20has%20a%20superb%20organisation%20that%20no%20party%20matches%2C%20and%20massive%20money%20and%20muscle%20power%20on%20account%20of%20its%20control%20over%20every%20organ%20of%20the%20state.%20Photo%3A%20X%2FBJP4India.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMuch%20of%20the%20analysis%20points%20in%20that%20direction%2C%20though%20it%20is%20noted%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DnXiYo-FlLKg%5C%22%3Ethe%20Congress%20held%20on%20to%20its%20assembly%20poll%20percentage%20of%202018%3C%2Fa%3E%20when%20it%20had%20wrested%20these%20three%20states%20from%20the%20BJP.%20In%20the%20recent%20era%2C%20that%20is%20unusual%20for%20the%20party%20when%20it%20is%20face-to-face%20with%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%20it%20nearly%20made%20it.%20Had%20the%20bid%20succeeded%2C%20it%20would%20have%20broken%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20tradition%20of%20not%20letting%20an%20incumbent%20return.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20losing%20side%2C%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20relatively%20high%20vote%20shares%20in%20the%20three%20north%20Indian%20states%20point%20to%20a%20new%20development%3A%20namely%2C%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20state%20leaders%20could%20hold%20their%20ground%20although%20they%20competed%20not%20against%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20state%20leaders%2C%20as%20may%20be%20expected%20in%20state%20elections%2C%20but%20against%20Modi%2C%20whose%20purported%20invincibility%20%E2%80%93%20and%20popularity%20%E2%80%93%20is%20so%20much%20the%20staple%20of%20media%20commentaries%20even%20out%20of%20season.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20upshot%20then%20is%20that%20with%20some%20actionable%20introspection%20on%20the%20part%20of%20the%20Congress%2C%20the%20party%20can%20possibly%20hold%20its%20own%20against%20Modi%20in%20these%20particular%20states%20even%20in%20the%20parliamentary%20election%2C%20which%20is%20barely%20five%20months%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20impression%20is%20bolstered%20by%20the%20fact%20that%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%20MP%20and%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20the%20BJP%20had%20already%20won%20practically%20all%20the%20seats%20in%20the%20last%20Lok%20Sabha%20poll.%20To%20reach%20the%20cent%20per%20cent%20mark%20in%20these%20states%2C%20the%20saffron%20party%20need%20only%20win%20three%20more%20seats%20while%20holding%20on%20to%20its%202019%20tally%20of%2062.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHow%20realistic%20is%20this%20when%20the%20Congress%20has%20shown%20it%20is%20cohesive%20enough%20to%20retain%20around%2040%25%20of%20the%20vote%20share%20in%20state%20elections%20in%20spite%20of%20the%20absence%20of%20%E2%80%98jointness%E2%80%99%2C%20to%20use%20a%20military%20term%2C%20in%20its%20ranks%20or%20in%20relation%20to%20allies%20or%20potential%20allies%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20a%20caveat%20here%20%E2%80%93%20that%20holding%2040%25%20of%20the%20vote%20in%20an%20assembly%20election%20does%20not%20guarantee%20winning%20the%20same%20vote%20share%20in%20the%20same%20state%20in%20a%20parliament%20poll%2C%20unless%20the%20body%20of%20supporters%20has%20turned%20unshakeable.%20That%20proposition%20remains%20to%20be%20tested.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FqXohhDbkOUs%3Fsi%3DyFgyxhCMe591Vnnx%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%2C%20there%20appears%20to%20be%20a%20whole%20new%20phenomenon%20on%20the%20horizon%20that%20all%20parties%20%E2%80%93%20not%20just%20the%20Congress%20%E2%80%93%20need%20to%20contend%20with%20or%20pay%20attention%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20that%20in%20the%20three%20states%20where%20the%20Congress%20lost%20recently%20%E2%80%93%20and%20in%20UP%2C%20which%20is%20electorally%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20most%20significant%20state%2C%20as%20it%20sends%20up%20the%20highest%20number%20of%20MPs%20to%20parliament%20%E2%80%93%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20leadership%20of%20the%20government%20and%20his%20total%20control%20of%20the%20BJP%20party%20apparatus%20appears%20to%20have%20wrought%20a%20cultural%20%3Cem%3Eputsch%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20or%20something%20akin%20to%20a%20cultural%20revolution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20any%20rate%2C%20in%20these%20regions%2C%20it%20has%20succeeded%20in%20creating%20a%20cultural%20rift%20that%20can%20be%20accelerated%20and%20catalysed%20into%20something%20resembling%20a%20revolution%20if%20Modi%20returns%20for%20a%20third%20five-year%20term.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rampant%20misuse%20of%20the%20levers%20of%20state%20power%20at%20all%20levels%20%E2%80%93%20from%20the%20panchayat%20office%20that%20the%20saffron%20party%20holds%20to%20the%20PM%E2%80%99s%20office%20%E2%80%93%20and%20social%20media%20propaganda%20on%20an%20unimaginable%20and%20uninterrupted%20scale%20to%20promote%20and%20further%20the%20perception%20of%20an%20idyllic%20past%20when%20there%20existed%20only%20Hindu%20society%20in%20India%2C%20now%20seems%20to%20find%20sympathetic%20acceptance%20among%20increasing%20numbers%20of%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECreating%20grounds%20for%20an%20embrace%20of%20Hindu-supremacist%20ideas%20are%20the%20essence%20of%20such%20a%20scheme.%20In%20this%20massive%20exercise%2C%20the%20emphasising%20of%20rituals%20in%20everyday%20life%2C%20and%20the%20re-adoption%20in%20daily%20practices%20of%20irrational%20beliefs%20and%20superstitions%20which%20appeared%20to%20be%20on%20the%20way%20out%2C%20are%20being%20undertaken%20as%20part%20of%20a%20plan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20experience%20of%20the%20present%20writer%2C%20this%20is%20all%20too%20evident%20in%20rural%20parts%20of%20the%20Hindi-speaking%20states.%20In%20this%20belt%2C%20the%20struggles%20of%20everyday%20life%20are%20harsh%20on%20account%20of%20deeper%20and%20more%20extensive%20poverty%2C%20and%20the%20penetration%20of%20modern%20ideas%20and%20culture%20%E2%80%93%20such%20as%20gender%20equality%2C%20rationality%20and%20democratic%20conduct%20%E2%80%93%20way%20slower%20than%20in%20many%20other%20parts%20of%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fhindi-urdu-hindutva-ram-temple-ayodhya-uttar-pradesh%5C%22%3EHindi-Hindu%20Nationalism%20and%20Secular%20Retreat%20in%20the%20Heartland%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20has%20made%20them%20prime%20catchment%20areas%20for%20the%20RSS%20and%20related%20bodies%2C%20including%20the%20BJP%2C%20whose%20stock-in-trade%20is%20some%20contrived%20notion%20of%20past%20greatness%2C%20single-religion%20nationalism%20and%20the%20bearing%20of%20overt%20signatures%20of%20allegiance%20to%20a%20particular%20belief%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiven%20the%20massive%20push%20in%20this%20broad%20direction%2C%20the%20finding%20in%20the%20CSDS-Lokniti%20surveys%20in%20respect%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Felections%2Fmadhya-pradesh-assembly%2Flokniti-csds-survey-a-look-at-the-modi-chouhan-influence-on-the-bjps-success-in-madhya-pradesh%2Farticle67611001.ece%5C%22%3EMP%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Felections%2Fchhattisgarh-assembly%2Ffrom-development-to-defamation-the-election-campaign-in-chhattisgarh%2Farticle67614809.ece%5C%22%3EChhattisgarh%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Felections%2Frajasthan-assembly%2Fbjp-versus-congress-a-clash-of-campaign-reach-and-impact%2Farticle67607277.ece%5C%22%3ERajasthan%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20substantial%20numbers%20of%20those%20surveyed%20(percentages%20vary%20in%20the%20different%20states)%20had%20made%20up%20their%20minds%20to%20vote%20for%20the%20BJP%20regardless%20of%20what%20the%20issues%20were%20and%20who%20would%20lead%20the%20campaign%2C%20though%20they%20agreed%20that%20unemployment%20and%20high%20prices%20were%20serious%20problems%20they%20faced%2C%20can%20occasion%20no%20surprise.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndeed%2C%20this%20can%20be%20said%20to%20be%20a%20pointer%20to%20the%20production%20of%20a%20carefully%20crafted%20cultural%20rift%20being%20well%20under%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlongside%20the%20emphasis%20on%20rituals%2C%20irrational%20beliefs%20and%20superstition%20in%20the%20name%20of%20tradition%20and%20culture%2C%20through%20massive%20high-dosage%20propaganda%20exist%20the%20legitimising%20of%20caste-based%20entitlements%20and%20also%20of%20a%20certain%20type%20of%20political%20ideas%2C%20as%20well%20as%20gossip%2C%20aimed%20at%20destroying%20the%20heritage%20of%20some%20leaders%20of%20the%20freedom%20movement%20and%20the%20first%20important%20leaders%20of%20post-independence%20India%2C%20in%20particular%20Nehru%20%E2%80%93%20and%20his%20legacy%20and%20ideas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThrough%20personal%20interactions%20over%20time%2C%20the%20present%20writer%20has%20also%20observed%20in%20rural%20areas%20the%20continuing%20and%20organised%20political%20assassination%20of%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%2C%20although%20the%20most%20senior%20leaders%20of%20the%20current%20establishment%20take%20care%20not%20to%20be%20associated%20with%20such%20activity%2C%20while%20known%20rabble-rouser%20BJP%20MPs%20are%20perhaps%20permitted%20to%20make%20no%20secret%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Funion-minister-giriraj-singh-says-godse-a-saput-of-india%5C%22%3Etheir%20admiration%20for%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20assassins%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EHello%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fharidwarpolice%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40haridwarpolice%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FAshokKumar_IPS%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40AshokKumar_IPS%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20What%20about%20this%20threat%20to%20Govt%E2%80%99s%20by%20Anand%20Swaroop%20Maharaj%20who%20s