0Hindu%20society%2C%20culture%20and%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESabyasachi%20Das%2C%20the%20young%20economics%20teacher%20who%20earlier%20this%20year%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feducation%2Fashoka-university-courses-sabyasachi-das%5C%22%3Eobliged%20to%20resign%20his%20position%20from%20Ashoka%20University%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20account%20of%20the%20impact%20of%20his%20academic%20paper%20that%20dealt%20with%20vote%20manipulation%20possibilities%20in%20closely%20contested%20constituencies%20in%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%2C%20does%20point%20to%20the%20suppression%20of%20the%20Muslim%20voter%2C%20although%20he%20notes%20that%20he%20looked%20at%20data%20only%20from%20eleven%20constituencies%20and%20was%20for%20that%20reason%20not%20reaching%20firm%20conclusions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20such%20an%20atmosphere%20of%20revived%20devotion%20to%20pre-modern%20ideas%20especially%20built%20up%20in%20the%20Modi%20era%2C%20the%20(Hindu)%20voter%20is%20far%20from%20impressed%20when%20a%20BJP%20opponent%20stands%20up%20and%20criticises%20the%20PM%E2%80%99s%20call%20to%20bang%20%3Cem%3Ethalis%20%3C%2Fem%3E(metal%20eating%20plates)%20to%20ward%20off%20the%20coronavirus%2C%20or%20when%20he%20claims%20ancient%20Hindus%20had%20mastered%20plastic%20surgery%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fworld%2F2014%2Foct%2F28%2Findian-prime-minister-genetic-science-existed-ancient-times%5C%22%3Ecites%20as%20proof%20Lord%20Ganesha%E2%80%99s%20elephant%20trunk%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20the%20magic%20being%20wrought%20through%20the%20cultural%20%3Cem%3Eputsch.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EWatch%20%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fvideo%2Fwatch-modi-has-largest-personality-cult-in-human-history-india-now-a-3070-democracy%5C%22%3EModi%20Has%20%E2%80%98Largest%20Personality%20Cult%20in%20Human%20History%E2%80%99%2C%20India%20Now%20a%2030%3A70%20Democracy%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20that%20matter%2C%20criticism%20of%20Modi%20for%20demonetisation%2C%20which%20ruined%20micro%20and%20small%20industries%20that%20are%20avenues%20of%20bulk%20employment%2C%20or%20faulty%20GST%20implementation%2C%20appear%20to%20cut%20no%20ice%20among%20significant%20sections%20of%20voters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20because%20Modi%20is%20seen%20by%20them%20as%20the%20central%20figure%20whose%20presence%20on%20the%20scene%20has%20made%20the%20%E2%80%98new%20present%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%93%20or%20in%20his%20own%20words%2C%20the%20%E2%80%9CNew%20India%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20possible%20even%20if%20the%20lives%20of%20the%20poor%20have%20suffered%20immeasurably%2C%20more%20than%20under%20any%20of%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20predecessors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20it%20is%20this%20facet%20of%20Modi%20that%20appears%20to%20make%20him%20%E2%80%9Cpopular%E2%80%9D%2C%20turning%20that%20term%20on%20its%20head.%20In%20ordinary%20usage%2C%20the%20expression%20connotes%20appeal%20deriving%20from%20the%20innate%20personal%20traits%20of%20a%20public%20figure%20%E2%80%93%20politician%2C%20sports%20icon%2C%20or%20film%20or%20rock%20star.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20newly%20constructed%20Ram%20temple%20is%20inaugurated%20in%20Ayodhya%20in%20January%2C%20just%20months%20before%20the%20national%20election%2C%20the%20reverberations%20of%20the%20event%20are%20expected%20to%20be%20felt%20far%20and%20wide%2C%20and%20not%20just%20in%20rural%20or%20%E2%80%98rurban%E2%80%99%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20our%20great%20cities%20too%2C%20millions%20of%20people%20from%20rural%20or%20semi-rural%20areas%20of%20the%20Hindi%20belt%20live%20in%20hard%20conditions%20to%20make%20a%20living.%20In%20their%20new%20%E2%80%98homes%E2%80%99%20they%20may%20be%20exposed%20to%20metropolitan%20culture%20in%20a%20variety%20of%20ways%2C%20but%20they%20are%20also%20exposed%20to%20gargantuan%20levels%20of%20%E2%80%98New%20India%E2%80%99%20propaganda%20which%20plays%20in%20the%20background%20twenty-four%20hours%20of%20the%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20mainstream%20media%20plays%20up%20the%20effect%20even%20further%2C%20providing%20%E2%80%98legitimacy%E2%80%99%20to%20what%20they%20happen%20to%20see%20on%20WhatsApp.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20in%20such%20a%20setting%20of%20election%20politics%20that%20the%20Congress%20party%20and%20its%20partners%20of%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20are%20required%20to%20forge%20their%20tactics%20and%20their%20strategies.%20The%20task%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20far%20from%20easy%2C%20although%20the%20difficulties%20are%20by%20no%20means%20insurmountable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F18132549%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-07-18-at-1.04.45-PM-1024x614.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F18132549%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-07-18-at-1.04.45-PM-1024x614.jpeg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F18132549%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-07-18-at-1.04.45-PM-300x180.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F18132549%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-07-18-at-1.04.45-PM.jpeg%201200w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-663754%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22504%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EPhoto%3A%20Special%20arrangement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20primary%20requirement%20is%20that%20the%20INDIA%20parties%20recognise%20that%20they%20are%20each%20an%20organic%20part%20of%20an%20alliance%20to%20which%20they%20formally%20subscribe.%20Security%20does%20lie%20in%20numbers%2C%20in%20mutual%20solidarity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20this%20is%20not%20grasped%2C%20and%20the%20day%20is%20lost%20when%20the%20results%20come%20in%20after%20the%20parliamentary%20poll%2C%20each%20member%20of%20the%20alliance%20will%20be%20made%20to%20hang%20separately.%20This%20may%20be%20taken%20to%20be%20%E2%80%9CModi%E2%80%99s%20guarantee%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20if%20genuine%20solidarity%20can%20be%20forged%2C%20even%20if%20this%20means%20some%20sacrificing%20for%20common%20good%20here%20and%20there%20by%20dominant%20parties%20in%20a%20region%2C%20the%20BJP%20can%20be%20pushed%20back%20in%20state%20after%20state%20in%20every%20part%20of%20north%20India%2C%20including%20the%20Hindi%20belt.%20A%20cursory%20view%20of%20the%20data%20for%20assembly%20and%20parliamentary%20elections%20for%20the%20recent%20period%20would%20point%20that%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVoting%20numbers%20in%20thrall%20of%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98New%20India%E2%80%99%20have%20grown%20steadily%20in%20recent%20years%2C%20but%20they%20are%20outdone%20in%20collective%20strength%20by%20a%20wide%20coalition%20of%20interests%20%E2%80%93%20farmers%2C%20farm%20workers%2C%20formal%20and%20informal%20sector%20workers%20and%20the%20wider%20intelligentsia.%20But%20there%20is%20a%20proviso.%20The%20appeal%20to%20these%20powerful%20sections%20must%20be%20made%20by%20the%20alliance%20parties%20acting%20in%20tandem%20and%20in%20coordination.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20INDIA%20grouping%E2%80%99s%20best%20chance%20may%20lie%20in%20reaching%20for%20the%20doable.%20This%20may%20boil%20down%20to%20reducing%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%93%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%93%20numbers%20in%20Gujarat%2C%20Assam%2C%20UP%2C%20MP%2C%20Chhattisgarh%20and%20Rajasthan%2C%20which%20have%20a%20total%20of%20around%20180%20parliament%20seats.%20This%20does%20not%20look%20like%20an%20impossible%20ask%20if%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20INDIA%20group%20leaders%20are%20united%20in%20their%20vision.%20That%20is%20key.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20the%20recent%20assembly%20election%2C%20when%20the%20various%20INDIA%20conclaves%20were%20held%2C%20each%20alliance%20party%20and%20the%20Congress%20in%20particular%20(being%20the%20largest%20party%2C%20and%20about%20to%20go%20into%20a%20one-to-one%20battle%20with%20the%20BJP)%2C%20was%20guilty%20of%20not%20underlining%20that%20their%20electoral%20association%2C%20which%20was%20in%20effect%20a%20political%20and%20ideological%20front%20against%20%E2%80%98New%20India%E2%80%99%2C%20had%20to%20be%20for%20national%20elections%20as%20well%20as%20state%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fwhy-2024-is-going-to-be-an-existential-fight-for-the-india-alliance%5C%22%3EWhy%202024%20Is%20Going%20to%20Be%20an%20Existential%20Fight%20for%20the%20INDIA%20Alliance%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20a%20senior%20Congress%20leader%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20who%20aimed%20at%20high%20office%2C%20took%20pains%20to%20exclude%20the%20assembly%20polls%20from%20the%20equation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20leadership%20was%20guilty%20of%20not%20obliging%20state%20leaders%20in%20all%20states%20where%20elections%20were%20being%20fought%20to%20see%20the%20larger%20picture%2C%20to%20take%20the%20extra%20step%20to%20reach%20an%20understanding%20with%20all%20sections%20of%20society%20and%20all%20parties%20that%20were%20not%20in%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20clasp%20%E2%80%93%20essentially%2C%20of%20abusing%20the%20latitude%20given%20to%20them%20and%20not%20falling%20in%20line%20on%20fundamental%20matters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20playing%20of%20the%20religion%20card%20by%20CM-aspirant%20Kamal%20Nath%20(although%20this%20was%20not%20communal%20since%20it%20was%20not%20aimed%20against%20any%20religion%20group)%20and%20thinking%20he%20had%20aced%20the%20game%2C%20was%20not%20worthy%20even%20of%20an%20amateur.%20Such%20a%20leader%20can%20hardly%20inspire%20confidence%20for%20planning%20moves%20for%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20poll.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Rajasthan%2C%20incumbent%20CM%20Ashok%20Gehlot%20remained%20selfishly%20all-knowing.%20He%20rejected%20sensible%20advice%20to%20deny%20nominations%20to%20many%20unpopular%20sitting%20MLAs%20only%20for%20the%20reason%20that%20they%20had%20sided%20with%20him%20in%20factional%20warfare%20earlier.%20Again%2C%20the%20central%20leadership%20let%20this%20pass%20instead%20of%20cracking%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20top%20leaders%20could%20also%20have%20ensured%20that%20Gehlot%20struck%20an%20understanding%20with%20the%20CPI(M)%20and%20the%20Bharat%20Adivasi%20Party.%20This%20may%20have%20just%20helped%20the%20Congress%20go%20over%20the%20line%2C%20as%20psephologists%20have%20suggested.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chhattisgarh%20CM%2C%20Bhupesh%20Baghel%2C%20overlooked%20Adivasi%20aspirations%20and%20flirted%20with%20the%20religion%20game.%20Regrettably%2C%20the%20Congress%20leadership%2C%20fearing%20the%20unknown%2C%20failed%20to%20act%20as%20effective%20monitor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20leadership%20question%20is%20straightforward%20in%20the%20non-Congress%20parties%20of%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%2C%20the%20elected%20Congress%20president%2C%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%2C%20seems%20to%20be%20in%20need%20of%20abler%20political%20all-round%20backroom%20support.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThrough%20the%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Yatra%2C%20former%20party%20president%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20has%20played%20his%20part%20by%20preparing%20the%20ground%20for%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99%20possible%20electoral%20revival.%20In%20an%20%3Cem%3Eavatar%3C%2Fem%3E%20as%20guide%20and%20consultant%2C%20he%20may%20be%20invaluable%20in%20formulating%20strategic%20communications%20strategies%20within%20his%20party%20and%20with%20alliance%20partners.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20Modi%20at%20the%20helm%20on%20the%20other%20side%2C%20the%20wall%20between%20state%20and%20national%20issues%20has%20collapsed.%20INDIA%20might%20benefit%20by%20continuing%20to%20project%20state%20issues%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%2C%20and%20steer%20clear%20of%20attacking%20individual%20leaders.%20A%20battle%20has%20been%20lost%2C%20a%20cultural%20blitzkrieg%20is%20on%2C%20but%20a%20war%20is%20more%20than%20one%20engagement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fanand-k-sahay%5C%22%3EAnand%20K.%20Sahay%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20political%20commentator%20based%20in%20New%20Delhi.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702825255000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F01145303%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-09-01-at-1.39.00-PM-1.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Findia-alliance-parties-after-the-defeat-preparing-for-2024%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Voting%20numbers%20in%20thrall%20of%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98New%20India%E2%80%99%20have%20grown%20steadily%2C%20but%20they%20are%20outdone%20in%20collective%20strength%20by%20a%20wide%20coalition%20of%20interests.%20The%20appeal%20to%20these%20powerful%20sections%20must%20be%20made%20by%20the%20alliance%20parties%20acting%20in%20tandem%20and%20coordination.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A17%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Findia-alliance-parties-after-the-defeat-preparing-for-2024%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bryon%20Allen%20on%20Continuing%20to%20Make%20%E2%80%98Strategic%20Acquisitions%E2%80%99%20in%20Television%3A%20%E2%80%98I%20Haven%E2%80%99t%20Yet%20Done%20What%20I%20Set%20Out%20to%20Do%E2%80%99%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702825200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2FBC-BYRON-ALLEN_MASTER.jpg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D563%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1235837147%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22When%20Byron%20Allen%20was%20just%2014%2C%20he%20started%20doing%20stand-up%20comedy.%20Four%20years%20later%2C%20in%201979%2C%20he%20became%20the%20youngest%20comedian%20to%20appear%20on%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Ton