-thakur-dance-their-heart-out-at-their-wedding-celebrations-ayushmann-khurrana-shakti-mohan-join-in-watch-unseen-video%2Farticleshow%2F106067118.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Film%20director%20Otar%20Iosseliani%20dies%20aged%2089%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702825010000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2FFDB3%2Fproduction%2F_132074946_gettyimages-483489510.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fentertainment-arts-67743328%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Georgian-born%20director%20is%20known%20for%20films%20such%20as%20Pastorale%20and%20Favourites%20of%20the%20Moon.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A650%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fentertainment-arts-67743328%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fentertainment-arts-67743328.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fentertainment-arts-67743328.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BChina's%20Xi%20Jinping%20Won't%20Forget...%26quot%3B%3A%20Ex-Army%20Chief%20On%202020%20Galwan%20Clash%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EChina%20followed%20%26quot%3Bwolf-warrior%20diplomacy%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bsalami-slicing%26quot%3B%20tactics%20with%20impunity%20browbeating%20smaller%20neighbours%20and%20it%20took%20the%20Indian%20Army%20to%20show%20to%20the%20world%20that%20%26quot%3Benough%20is%20enough%26quot%3B%20and%20challenge%20the%20%26quot%3Bneighbourhood%20bully%26quot%3B%2C%20says%20Gen%20Manoj%20Mukund%20Naravane%2C%20the%2028th%20Chief%20of%20Army%20Staff%2C%20recounting%20the%20Indian%20response%20to%20the%20Chinese%20aggression%20in%20Eastern%20Ladakh%20in%202020.%3Cbr%3E%5CnIn%20his%20memoirs%20'Four%20Stars%20of%20Destiny'%2C%20Naravane%2C%20providing%20a%20rare%20insight%20into%20the%20deadly%20Galwan%20Valley%20clashes%2C%20says%20Chinese%20President%20Xi%20Jinping%20will%20not%20forget%20June%2016%20any%20time%20soon%20as%20China's%20People's%20Liberation%20Army%20suffered%20%26quot%3Bfatal%20casualties%26quot%3B%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20over%20two%20decades%20in%20the%20fighting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENaravane%2C%20one%20of%20the%20foremost%20Army%20Generals%2C%20provided%20a%20gripping%20account%20of%20the%20India-China%20confrontation%20before%20and%20after%20the%20deadly%20Galwan%20Valley%20incident%2C%20India's%20overall%20response%20to%20the%20Chinese%20action%20and%20how%20it%20served%20as%20a%20catalyst%20to%20firm%20up%20the%20Army's%20combat%20readiness%20along%20the%20Line%20of%20Actual%20Control%20(LAC).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20one%20of%20the%20saddest%20days%20of%20my%20entire%20career%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Naravane%20recalling%20the%20death%20of%2020%20Army%20personnel%20in%20the%20Galwan%20Valley%20clashes%20in%20June%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20tenure%20as%20the%20Army%20Chief%20from%20December%2031%2C%202019%20to%20April%2030%2C%202022%20was%20primarily%20marked%20by%20the%20Chinese%20challenges%20along%20the%20contested%20border%20as%20well%20as%20the%20rolling%20out%20of%20long-term%20reform%20measures%20to%20enhance%20the%20combat%20capabilities%20of%20the%20force.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJune%2016%20is%20(Chinese%20President)%20Xi%20Jinping's%20birthday.%20This%20is%20not%20a%20day%20he%20will%20forget%20any%20time%20soon.%20For%20the%20first%20time%20in%20over%20two%20decades%2C%20the%20Chinese%20and%20the%20PLA%20had%20suffered%20fatal%20casualties%2C%26quot%3B%20Naravane%20writes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20had%20been%20following%20wolf-warrior%20diplomacy%20and%20salami-slicing%20tactics%20everywhere%20with%20impunity%2C%20browbeating%20smaller%20neighbours%20like%20Nepal%20and%20Bhutan%2C%20while%20staking%20their%20ever-increasing%20claims%20in%20the%20South%20China%20Sea%2C%20without%20having%20to%20pay%20any%20costs%2C%20especially%20in%20terms%20of%20human%20lives.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BIt%20took%20India%20and%20the%20Indian%20Army%20to%20show%20to%20the%20world%20that%20enough%20is%20enough%20and%20to%20challenge%20the%20neighbourhood%20bully.%26quot%3B%20Delving%20into%20the%20overall%20situation%20along%20the%20frontier%2C%20Naravane%2C%20at%20the%20same%20time%2C%20suggests%20having%20a%20%26quot%3Bnon-aggression%26quot%3B%20pact%20between%20the%20two%20countries%20pending%20the%20settlement%20of%20the%20overall%20boundary%20dispute%2C%20saying%20it%20would%20go%20a%20long%20way%20in%20restoring%20confidence%20and%20pave%20the%20way%20for%20de-escalation%20and%20de-induction%20of%20forces.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E'Four%20Stars%20of%20Destiny'%20published%20by%20Penguin%20Random%20House%20India%20will%20hit%20the%20stands%20next%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20Galwan%20Valley%20incident%2C%20Naravane%20says%20it%20occurred%20in%20view%20of%20the%20Chinese%20PLA%20refusing%20to%20remove%20two%20tents%20that%20it%20had%20erected%20in%20Patrolling%20Point%2014%20(PP-14)%2C%20adding%20following%20the%20adversary's%20refusal%2C%20the%20Indian%20Army%20decided%20to%20pitch%20its%20own%20tents%20in%20the%20same%20general%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20eastern%20Ladakh%20border%20row%20began%20in%20May%202020.%20Naravane%20says%20flag-level%20meetings%20had%20been%20continuing%20at%20other%20locations%20then%2C%20including%20at%20PP-15%20and%20PP-17A%2C%20where%20troops%20fell%20back%20over%20agreed%20distances%2C%20thereby%20reducing%20the%20chances%20of%20violent%20face-offs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20PP-14%2C%20however%2C%20whenever%20we%20asked%20the%20PLA%20to%20remove%20their%20tents%2C%20they%20kept%20changing%20their%20stance.%20From%20'some%20more%20time%20was%20needed'%2C%20to%20'we%20will%20check%20with%20our%20superiors'%2C%20to%20it%20'being%20beyond%20the%20mandate%20of%20the%20talks'.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BFrom%20this%20stonewalling%2C%20it%20became%20evident%20that%20there%20had%20been%20no%20intention%20of%20removing%20those%20tents%20in%20the%20first%20place.%20To%20counter%20this%2C%20we%20also%20decided%20to%20pitch%20our%20own%20tents%20in%20the%20same%20general%20area%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20writes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENaravane%20says%20when%20Indian%20Army%20personnel%20went%20to%20pitch%20the%20tents%2C%20there%20was%20a%20violent%20reaction%20from%20the%20Chinese%20side.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCol%20Santosh%20Babu%2C%20Commanding%20Officer%20of%2016%20BIHAR%2C%20went%20forward%20with%20a%20small%20party%20of%20troops%20to%20attempt%20to%20defuse%20the%20situation%20but%20the%20PLA%20were%20in%20no%20mood%20to%20relent%20and%20attacked%20the%20CO's%20party%20too%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThereafter%2C%20it%20became%20a%20free-for-all.%20With%20darkness%20setting%20in%2C%20both%20sides%20rushed%20in%20additional%20troops%20and%20a%20see-saw%20engagement%20continued%20throughout%20the%20night%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20recounts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20armed%2C%20neither%20side%20opened%20fire%2C%20instead%20using%20batons%20or%20clubs%20and%20throwing%20or%20rolling%20down%20stones%20on%20each%20other's%20positions%2C%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20Army%20Chief%20says%20due%20to%20better%20connectivity%20on%20their%20side%2C%20the%20PLA%20were%20able%20to%20move%20troops%20forward%20in%20armoured%20personnel%20carriers%20which%20changed%20the%20balance%20in%20their%20favour.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENaravane%20says%20he%20told%20then%20Northern%20Army%20Commander%20Lt%20Gen%20YK%20Joshi%20during%20a%20phone%20call%20at%201%3A30%20am%20on%20June%2016%20that%20the%20Army%20must%20hit%20back%20and%20make%20the%20PLA%20pay%20the%20price%20for%20their%20misadventure.%20%26quot%3BDaylight%20revealed%20a%20not-so-favourable%20situation.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BFew%20jawans%20who%20could%20not%20make%20it%20back%20at%20night%20or%20who%20had%20been%20separated%20started%20trickling%20back.%20Five%20jawans%20had%20died%20of%20injuries%20in%20the%20melee.%20The%20next%20morning%2C%20as%20the%20head%20count%20was%20taken%2C%20we%20realised%20many%20were%20missing%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20tense%20negotiations%20began%2C%20many%20of%20our%20boys%2C%20who%20had%20either%20got%20disoriented%20or%20had%20been%20briefly%20detained%20by%20the%20PLA%20without%20food%20or%20medical%20aid%2C%20returned%20to%20base%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHowever%2C%2015%20of%20them%20succumbed%20to%20the%20combined%20effects%20of%20their%20injuries%20and%20hypothermia.%20It%20was%20one%20of%20the%20saddest%20days%20of%20my%20entire%20career.%26quot%3B%20The%20Galwan%20Valley%20clashes%20on%20June%2015%2C%202020%20marked%20the%20most%20serious%20military%20conflicts%20between%20India%20and%20China%20in%20decades%20and%20the%20full%20extent%20of%20the%20deadliest%20confrontation%20was%20known%20the%20next%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20in%20a%20profession%20where%20death%20is%20always%20lurking%20around%20the%20corner.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEvery%20patrol%20or%20ambush%20can%20be%20your%20last.%20As%20a%20Company%20and%20Battalion%20Commander%2C%20my%20unit%20had%20suffered%20casualties%2C%20and%20I%20was%20always%20stoic%20in%20the%20face%20of%20adversity%20or%20bad%20news.%20Yet%2C%20losing%2020%20men%20in%20a%20day%20was%20hard%20to%20bear%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20notes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbout%20the%20casualties%20on%20the%20Chinese%20side%2C%20Naravane%20says%20it%20was%20evident%20that%20they%20%26quot%3Btoo%20suffered%20substantially%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20men%20who%20were%20in%20Chinese%20hands%20had%20been%20kept%20out%20in%20the%20open%20and%20they%20had%20seen%20several%20bodies%20being%20fished%20out%20of%20the%20river.%20Whenever%20that%20happened%2C%20they%20were%20subjected%20to%20a%20fresh%20round%20of%20beatings%2C%26quot%3B%20Naravane%20writes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20sheer%20savagery%20of%20their%20response%20was%20in%20itself%20indicative%20of%20the%20losses%20they%20had%20suffered.%20Initially%2C%20they%20did%20not%20admit%20to%20any%20casualties%20at%20all%3B%20then%20many%20months%20later%2C%20admitted%20to%20four%20or%20five%20killed%2C%20including%20the%20CO%20on%20their%20side%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENaravane%20also%20mentioned%20a%20report%20by%20a%20group%20of%20Australian%20researchers%20that%20put%20the%20figure%20of%20Chinese%20fatalities%20to%20at%20least%2038%2C%20A%20separate%20Russian%20(TASS)%20report%20put%20the%20figure%20closer%20to%2045%20killed%2C%20which%20was%20consistent%20with%20other%20intelligence%20reports%2C%20including%20those%20from%20the%20US%2C%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENaravane%20says%20the%20time%20is%20ripe%20for%20the%20resumption%20of%20the%20special-representative%20level%20talks%20to%20settle%20the%20border%20question%20between%20the%20two%20sides.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPending%20the%20settlement%20of%20the%20boundary%20dispute%2C%20which%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20time-consuming%2C%20articulation%20of%20a%20'non-aggression'%20pact%20between%20the%20two%20countries%20would%20go%20a%20long%20way%20in%20restoring%20confidence%2C%20paving%20the%20way%20for%20de-escalation%20and%20de-induction%20of%20forces%20from%20Tibet%2FLadakh%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSuch%20a%20pact%20would%20be%20somewhat%20akin%20to%20what%20China%20and%20the%20ASEAN%20countries%20are%20attempting%20to%20formalise%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20Army%20Chief%20says%20the%20crisis%20in%20eastern%20Ladakh%20served%20as%20a%20catalyst%20for%20the%20Army's%20rebalancing%20to%20the%20northern%20front.%20The%20Army%20moved%20many%20key%20units%20to%20the%20northern%20front%20from%20other%20parts%20following%20the%20Chinese%20aggression.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThough%20still%20inadequate%2C%20the%20increase%20in%20force%20ratios%20on%20the%20Northern%20Front%20will%20definitely%20make%20the%20PLA%20think%20twice%20before%20embarking%20on%20any%20misadventure%2C%20especially%20now%20that%20we%20have%20the%20offensive%20capability%20to%20take%20the%20battle%20into%20Chinese%20territory%2C%26quot%3B%20Naravane%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20our%20posture%20against%20China%2C%20we%20have%20moved%20up%20from%20dissuasive%20deterrence%20(defensive)%20to%20credible%20deterrence%20(offensive%20defence).%20With%20these%20developments%2C%20the%20PLA%20must%20have%20realised%20that%20a%20military%20solution%20to%20the%20border%20problem%20is%20improbable%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E'Wolf-warrior'%20diplomacy%20is%20a%20term%20used%20for%20a%20kind%20of%20assertive%20diplomacy.%20Salami%20Slicing%20is%20a%20tactic%20used%20to%20capture%20territory%20piece%20by%20piece.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702824900000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-01%2Fu52mqcoo_army-chief-general-mm-naravane-ani_625x300_14_January_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchinas-xi-jinping-wont-forget-ex-army-chief-mm-naravane-on-2020-galwan-clash-4691753%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22China%20followed%20%26quot%3Bwolf-warrior%20diplomacy%26quot%3B%20with%20impunity%20browbeating%20smaller%20neighbours%20and%20it%20took%20the%20Indian%20Army%20to%20show%20to%20the%20world%20that%20%26quot%3Benough%20is%20enough%26quot%3B%20and%20challenge%20the%20%26quot%3Bneighbourhood%20bully%26quot%3B%2C%20says%20Gen%20Manoj%20Mukund%20Naravane.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchinas-xi-jinping-wont-forget-ex-army-chief-mm-naravane-on-2020-galwan-clash-4691753%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchinas-xi-jinping-wont-forget-ex-army-chief-mm-naravane-on-2020-galwan-clash-4691753%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchinas-xi-jinping-wont-forget-ex-army-chief-mm-naravane-on-2020-galwan-clash-4691753%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Thousands%20flee%20as%20paramilitaries%20gain%20ground%20in%20Sudan%20aid%20hub%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702824625000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-106067160%2Cimgsize-163422.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fthousands-flee-as-paramilitaries-gain-ground-in-sudan-aid-hub%2Farticleshow%2F106067085.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F106067085.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EParamilitary%20forces%20established%20a%20base%20Sunday%20in%20the%20formerly%20safe%20city%20of%20Wad%20Madani%20in%20war-correspondent%20reported%2C%20sending%20thousands%20fleeing%2C%20many%20of%20them%20already%20displaced.%20Thousands%20have%20sought%20to%20escape%20the%20former%20aid%20hub%20since%20the%20war%20between%20the%20army%20and%20the%20paramilitary%20Rapid%20Support%20Forces%20(RSF)%20reached%20Wad%20Madani%20on%20Friday%2C%20according%20to%20the%20United%20Nations.%20Previously%2C%20the%20city%20had%20been%20%26quot%3Bone%20of%20Sudan's%20few%20remaining%20sanctuaries%26quot%3B%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Norwegian%20Refugee%20Council's%20Sudan%20director%20William%20Carter.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fthousands-flee-as-paramilitaries-gain-ground-in-sudan-aid-hub%2Farticleshow%2F106067085.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22