-healthy-growth-123121700663_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fsbi-slows-down-unsecured-retail-loans-to-focus-on-healthy-growth-123121700663_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BLike%20Passenger%20In%20Bus%26quot%3B%3A%20S%20Jaishankar's%20Sharp%20Dig%20At%20UN%20Security%20Council%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ETaking%20a%20sharp%20dig%20at%20the%20United%20Nations%20Security%20Council%2C%20External%20Affairs%20Minister%20S%20Jaishankar%20said%20that%20it%20is%20like%20an%20%26quot%3Bold%20club%26quot%3B%20where%20member%20nations%20are%20unwilling%20to%20admit%20new%20members%20as%20they%20perceive%20it%20as%20losing%20the%20grip.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20address%20at%20the%20Rotary%20Institute%202023%20event%20in%20Bengaluru%20on%20Sunday%2C%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20said%20that%20the%20members%20of%20the%20%26quot%3Bclub%26quot%3B%20do%20not%20want%20their%20practices%20to%20be%20questioned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSecurity%20Council%20is%20like%20an%20old%20club%2C%20where%20there%20are%20set%20members%20who%20don't%20want%20to%20let%20go%20of%20the%20grip.%20They%20want%20to%20keep%20control%20over%20the%20club.%20Not%20very%20keen%20to%20admit%20more%20members%2C%20not%20keen%20to%20have%20their%20practices%20questioned%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECalling%20it%20a%20failure%2C%20the%20External%20Affairs%20Minister%20pointed%20out%20that%20with%20no%20reforms%2C%20the%20UN%20is%20getting%20less%20and%20less%20effective.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20a%20way%2C%20it's%20a%20human%20failing.%20But%20I%20think%20today%20it%20is%20harming%20the%20world.%20It%20is%20harming%20the%20world%20because%2C%20on%20key%20issues%20confronting%20the%20world%2C%20the%20UN%20is%20getting%20less%20and%20less%20effective%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20I%20can%20also%20tell%20you%20the%20global%20sentiment.%20I%20mean%2C%20today%2C%20if%20you%20ask%20200%20countries%20in%20the%20world%2C%20do%20you%20want%20reform%20or%20don't%20you%20want%20reform%3F%20A%20very%20large%20number%20of%20countries%20would%20say%2C%20yes%2C%20we%20want%20reform...%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20while%20emphasising%20that%20nations%20are%20urging%20for%20reforms%20efforts%20in%20the%20UN%20Security%20Council%20to%20deal%20with%20the%20prevailing%20challenges.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20in%20September%2C%20External%20Affairs%20Minister%20S%20Jaishankar%20said%20that%20the%20resistance%20of%20the%20United%20Nations%20to%20reform%20its%20structure%2C%20will%20eventually%20lead%20to%20the%20body%20being%20%26quot%3Banachronistic%26quot%3B%20and%20people%20will%20start%20finding%20solutions%20outside.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Jaishankar%20gave%20an%20%26quot%3Binjudicious%26quot%3B%20reference%20of%20passengers%20sitting%20in%20a%20bus%20drawing%20a%20comparison%20with%20the%20permanent%20members%20of%20the%20UN%20Security%20Council.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20somewhere%20injudiciously...described%20it%20like%20a%20passenger%20in%20a%20bus.%20A%20person%20sitting%20on%20the%20seat%2C%20will%20not%20vacate%20it%20for%20the%20next%20person.%20So%20there%20are%20these%20five%20guys%20sitting.%20Sometimes%2C%20you%20see%20such%20passengers%2C%20you%20see%20someone%20is%20tired%2C%20someone%20is%20carrying%20a%20baby%2C%20they%20will%20not%20get%20up%20and%20give%20up%20that%20seat%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20reforms%20in%20the%20global%20systems%20have%20been%20an%20issue%20continuously%20raised%20by%20India%20and%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20on%20the%20global%20stage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20his%20concluding%20address%20at%20the%20G20%20Leaders%20Summit%20here%20in%20the%20national%20capital%2C%20PM%20Modi%20reiterated%20his%20stance%20of%20making%20global%20systems%20in%20accordance%20with%20the%20%26quot%3Brealities%20of%20the%20present%26quot%3B%20and%20t