y%20from%20him%20when%20he%20lands%20in%20India%2C%20The%20Straits%20Times%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20it%20is%20not%20illegal%20in%20Singapore%20for%20travellers%20to%20carry%20precious%20metals%2C%20including%20gold%2C%20out%20of%20the%20country%2C%20the%20couriers%20risk%20breaking%20the%20law%20in%20India%20when%20they%20do%20not%20declare%20the%20gold%20they%20are%20carrying%20in%2C%20the%20report%20quoted%20Mohamed%20Bilal%2C%20president%20of%20the%20Gem%20Traders%20Association%20of%20Singapore%2C%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMale%20Indian%20nationals%20are%20permitted%20to%20carry%20up%20to%2020%20gram%20of%20duty-free%20gold%2C%20of%20a%20maximum%20value%20of%20Rs%2050%2C000%20rupees%20(SGD%20800)%2C%20into%20India.%20The%20limit%20for%20female%20Indian%20nationals%20is%20double%20in%20terms%20of%20weight%20and%20value.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGold%20jewellery%20carried%20over%20and%20above%20these%20limits%20will%20attract%20customs%20duty.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBilal%20said%20that%20the%20practice%20of%20smuggling%20gold%20through%20'mules'%20has%20been%20going%20on%20for%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGold%20smuggling%20runners%20at%20Terminal%201%20of%20the%20Changi%20Airport%20want%20the%20'mules'%20to%20carry%20jewellery%20of%20between%2025%20gram%20and%2030%20gram%20of%20gold%2C%20which%20is%20just%20outside%20the%20legal%20limit%2C%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20report%20said%2C%20Indian%20authorities%2C%20including%20customs%20officials%2C%20are%20on%20the%20lookout%20for%20travellers%20acting%20as%20gold%20mules.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20comes%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20a%20spike%20in%20gold%20smuggling%20to%20the%20country%2C%20and%20amid%20reports%20of%20syndicates%20targeting%20travellers%20at%20various%20airports%20in%20jurisdictions%20in%20the%20Gulf%2C%20as%20well%20as%20in%20Asia%2C%20including%20Malaysia%20and%20Singapore%2C%20where%20gold%20is%20cheaper%20than%20in%20India%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20no%20weight%20limit%20on%20the%20amount%20of%20gold%20and%20other%20precious%20metals%20that%20can%20be%20transported%20out%20of%20Singapore%20by%20travellers%2C%20the%20report%20said%2C%20quoting%20Singapore%20Police%20Force.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20India%2C%20the%20world's%20second-biggest%20gold%20consumer%2C%20one%20gram%20of%2024%20karat%20gold%20costs%20about%20SGD%2099%20(approx%20Rs%206%2C177).%20It%20would%20cost%20about%20SGD%2092.40%20(approx%20Rs%205%2C765)%20in%20Singapore.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702817040000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Ffrn3llc8_gold-generic_625x300_17_December_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findian-migrant-workers-used-as-gold-mules-by-singapore-smugglers-report-4690435%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Smugglers%20in%20Singapore%20have%20been%20approaching%20Indian%20migrant%20workers%20flying%20home%20via%20Changi%20Airport%20to%20act%20as%20'gold%20mules'%20by%20carrying%20jewellery%20in%20exchange%20for%20a%20fee%2C%20according%20to%20a%20media%20report%20on%20Sunday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findian-migrant-workers-used-as-gold-mules-by-singapore-smugglers-report-4690435%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findian-migrant-workers-used-as-gold-mules-by-singapore-smugglers-report-4690435%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findian-migrant-workers-used-as-gold-mules-by-singapore-smugglers-report-4690435%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22European%20diplomacy%20steps%20up%20calls%20for%20Gaza%20cease-fire%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%2