%20old%20rooster%2C%20while%20too%20damaged%20to%20reuse%2C%20was%20saved%20from%20the%202019%20fire%2C%20giving%C2%A0the%20community%20hope.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThat%20there%20was%20hope%2C%20that%20not%20everything%20was%20lost.%20The%20beauty%20of%20the%20%5Bold%5D%20battered%20rooster%20%5B%E2%80%A6%5D%20expressed%20the%20cry%20of%20the%20cathedral%20suffering%20in%20flames%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F17162624%2FOld-rooster.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22640%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F17162624%2FOld-rooster.jpg%20640w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F17162624%2FOld-rooster-300x225.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-689562%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThe%20old%20rooster%20on%20the%20cathedral%E2%80%99s%20spire%20while%20it%20still%20stood.%20Photo%3A%20Panageotean%20Graphics%2FWikimedia%20Commons.%20CC%20BY-SA%204.0.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSince%20%5Bthe%20fire%5D%2C%C2%A0we%20have%20worked%20on%20this%20rooster%C2%A0successor%2C%20which%20sees%20the%20flame%20carried%20to%20the%20top%20of%20the%20cathedral%20as%20it%20was%20before%2C%20more%20than%2096%20meters%20from%20the%20ground%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20a%20fire%20of%20resurrection.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rooster%20marks%20the%20return%20of%20the%20day%20and%20is%20also%20a%20commonly%20used%20symbol%20in%C2%A0France%2C%20especially%20as%20a%20mark%20of%20Christ%E2%80%99s%20resurrection.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhen%20will%20reconstruction%20be%20completed%3F%3C%2Fstr