ose%20left%20in%20my%20life.%20Kindly%20permit%20me%20to%20end%20my%20life%20in%20a%20dignified%20way.%20Let%20my%20life%20be%3A%20dismissed.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EA%20woman%20civil%20judge%20(junior%20division)%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20has%20sent%20shockwaves%20in%20the%20judicial%20circles%20after%20she%20penned%20a%20disturbing%20open%20letter%20to%20the%20topmost%20judge%20in%20the%20country%20to%20allow%20her%20to%20take%20her%20own%20life.%20Her%20grievance%3A%20she%20alleges%20that%20she%20was%20sexually%20harassed%20by%20a%20district%20judge%20and%20his%20associates%3B%20despite%20her%20following%20the%20proper%20procedure%20and%20knocking%20on%20the%20doors%20of%20all%20the%20higher%20courts%2C%20she%20has%20not%20been%20able%20to%20secure%20justice%20for%20herself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20letter%2C%20written%20in%20%E2%80%9Cextreme%20pain%20and%20despair%2C%E2%80%9D%20is%20addressed%20to%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20D.Y.%20Chandrachud.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EAfter%20the%20letter%20was%20widely%20shared%20on%20social%20media%20on%20Friday%2C%20December%2015%2C%20CJI%20Chandrachud%20sought%20a%20status%20report%20from%20the%20administration%20of%20the%20Allahabad%20high%20court%20on%20the%20inquiry%20being%20conducted%20into%20allegations%20of%20sexual%20harassment%20raised%20by%20the%20woman%20judge.%20The%20CJI%20is%20yet%20to%20publicly%20respond%20to%20the%20matter%20or%20issue%20directions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ENo%20system%20of%20redressal%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9CI%20have%20been%20sexually%20harassed%20by%20one%20particular%20district%20judge%20and%20his%20associates.%20I%20was%20told%20to%20meet%20the%20district%20judge%20at%20night%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20civil%20judge%20wrote%20in%20her%20letter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EAlthough%20she%20does%20not%20state%20specific%20instance