0are%20cultivated%2C%20Sanjay%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CFirst%2C%20we%20source%20good%20quality%20oysters.%20Then%2C%20we%20perform%20minor%20surgery%20to%20implant%20plain%20or%20designed%20pearls%20%5Ban%20artificial%20nucleus%5D%20into%20the%20tissue%20of%20a%20pearl%20oyster.%20The%20oyster%20is%20closed%20and%20is%20kept%20on%20antibiotics%20inside%20a%20smaller%20water%20tank%20for%20two%20to%20three%20days%20and%20then%20shifted%20to%20a%20bigger%20pond.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20oyster%20then%20secretes%20nacre%20%5Ba%20form%20of%20calcium%20carbonate%5D%20around%20the%20nucleus.%20The%20pearls%20get%20readied%20to%20be%20harvested%20in%2012%20to%2014%20months%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESanjay%20shares%20tips%20on%20how%20to%20start%20oyster%20pearl%20farming%20for%20beginners%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20to%20identify%20good%20oysters%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ESanjay%20says%20that%20it%20is%20much%20easier%20to%20cultivate%20oysters%20and%20earn%20a%20decent%20income%20provided%20you%20cultivate%20good%20quality%20oysters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSource%20good%20quality%20oysters%20to%20get%20A-grade%20quality%20pearls.%20The%20size%20of%20the%20oyster%20should%20be%20between%202.5%20to%203%20inches.%20Its%20outer%20cover%20should%20be%20golden%20in%20colour%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKnow%20the%20market%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ESanjay%20highlights%20that%20usually%20%E2%80%98designer%20debris%E2%80%99%20or%20%E2%80%98irritants%E2%80%99%20in%20the%20shape%20of%20Hindu%20deities%20Ganesha%2C%20Rama%2C%20Shiva%2C%20the%20Ashoka%20Chakra%2C%20786%20(holy%20number%20in%20Islam)%2C%20Chhatrapati%20Shivaji%20Maharaj%2C%20etc%20are%20implanted%20in%20the%20oyster.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20final%20pearls%20come%20out%20in%20the%20shape%20of%20these%20symbols%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%20Sanjay%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CYou%20should%20be%20informed%20about%20the%20market%20demand.%20If%20you%20implant%20the%20nucleus%20of%20Ganesh%20%3Cem%3Eji%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20and%20go%20to%20sell%20in%20a%20Ram%20temple%2C%20then%20it%20would%20not%20be%20profitable.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Foyster-3-1700658917.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sanjay%20highlights%20that%20usually%20%E2%80%98designer%20debris%E2%80%99%20in%20the%20shape%20of%20Hindu%20deities%2C%20the%20Ashoka%20Chakra%2C%20786%2C%20etc%20are%20implanted%20in%20the%20oyster.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Foyster-3-1700658917.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Foyster-3-1700658917-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Foyster-3-1700658917-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Foyster-3-1700658917-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Foyster-3-1700658917-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-334677%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESanjay%20highlights%20that%20usually%20%E2%80%98designer%20debris%E2%80%99%20in%20the%20shape%20of%20Hindu%20deities%2C%20the%20Ashoka%20Chakra%2C%20786%2C%20etc%20are%20implanted%20in%20the%20oyster.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMaster%20the%20easier%20surgery%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ESanjay%20says%20that%20there%20are%20several%20types%20of%20surgical%20procedures%20in%20pearl%20cultures%20%E2%80%94%20like%20gonadal%20implantation%2C%20mantle%20tissue%20implantation%2C%20and%20mantle%20cavity%20insertion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20suggest%20that%20farmers%20learn%20mantle%20tissue%20surgery%20as%20it%20is%20easier%20to%20perform%20and%20the%20chances%20of%20oysters%20are%20higher%20as%20compared%20to%20other%20kinds%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPrepare%20the%20pond%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ESanjay%20informs%20that%20it%20is%20important%20to%20provide%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F267186%2Fpearl-farming-cultivation-oyster-shell-home-made-pond-set-up-ashok-manwani-kuljana%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eriver-like%20ecosystem%20%3C%2Fa%3Efor%20oysters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COysters%20should%20not%20feel%20alienated%20and%20that%20they%20are%20outside%20a%20river.%20They%20must%20have%20a%20river-like%20environment%20to%20thrive.%20To%20ensure%20this%2C%20you%20must%20introduce%20algae%20inside%20the%20pond.%20Algae%20is%20the%20major%20food%20source%20of%20an%20oyster%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECheck%20the%20pH%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ESanjay%20points%20out%20that%20farmers%20should%20ensure%20a%20pH%20of%20eight%20inside%20the%20water%20tank.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20pH%20is%20more%20than%20eight%20(alkaline)%2C%20oysters%20will%20not%20survive.%20You%20should%20also%20check%20pH%20levels%20weekly.%20If%20the%20pH%20is%20higher%2C%20keep%20changing%20the%20water.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20you%20have%20a%2020%C3%9720%20square%20feet%20pond%20with%2010%20feet%20depth%2C%20it%20would%20have%20the%20capacity%20to%20store%20one%20lakh%20litre%20water.%20So%2C%20you%20should%20replace%20at%20least%2010%2C000%20litres%20of%20water%20in%20every%20batch%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMaintain%20the%20temperature%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EGiven%20its%20geography%2C%20Sanjay%20says%20that%20Osmanabad%20has%20a%20fluctuating%20temperature%20between%2020%20and%2040%20degrees%20throughout%20the%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20oyster%20pearl%20farming%2C%20we%20must%20ensure%20a%20temperature%20of%2032%20degrees%20Celsius.%20It%20should%20not%20exceed%2035%20degrees.%20We%20have%20externally%20used%20aerators%20to%20regulate%20the%20temperature%20inside%20the%20water%20bank.%20It%20also%20boosts%20fresh%20algae%20growth%20and%20provides%20new%20micronutrients%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20All%20photos%3A%20Sanjay%20Pawar%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700662267000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Foyster-5-1700660441.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D334671%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Having%20incurred%20huge%20losses%20because%20of%20recurring%20droughts%2C%2010%20farmers%20from%20Osmanabad%2C%20Maharashtra%2C%20switched%20to%20oyster%20pearl%20farming%20to%20reap%20profits.%20One%20of%20the%20farmers%2C%20Sanjay%20Pawar%20shares%20six%20tips%20for%20beginners.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A15%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F334671%2Fmaharashtra-farmers-oyster-pearl-cultivation-battle-drought-suicide-earn-income%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20Colours%20of%20Hope%3A%20%E2%80%98My%20Daughter%2C%20A%20Bharatnatyam%20Dancer%2C%20Was%20Told%20She%E2%80%99ll%20Never%20Walk%20Nor%20Hear%E2%80%99%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EUjjwala%20Sahane%20and%20her%20husband%20were%20excited%20to%20start%20their%20family%20in%201985%20when%20they%20were%20blessed%20with%20a%20baby%20girl.%20Things%20were%20wonderful%20until%20their%20baby%20had%20a%20fall%20when%20she%20was%20six%20months%20old%2C%20which%20left%20her%20paralysed%20and%20permanently%20damaged%20her%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F334578%2Fcoda-child-of-deaf-adult-indian-sign-language-isl%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehearing%20centre%3C%2Fa%3E.%